<p><a href="#18">18. Eighty Percent of Respondents Said They Had Stopped Doing Business with a Company Because of Poor Customer Experience (HubSpot)</a></p>



<p><a href="#19">19. Fifty-One Percent of Consumers Trust Companies Who Make It Easy for Visitors to Contact the People behind the Company (KPMG)</a></p>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<h2><strong>Part 1: Demographics</strong></h2>



<h3 id="1"><strong>1. There Were 1.8 Billion Global Digital Buyers in 2018 (</strong><a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/251666/number-of-digital-buyers-worldwide/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><strong>Statista</strong></a><strong>)</strong></h3>



<p>As of writing, there are<a href="http://www.theworldcounts.com/counters/shocking_environmental_facts_and_statistics/world_population_clock_live" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"> 7.7 billion</a> people in the World.&nbsp;</p>



<p>That means 21.55 percent of the World’s population buy online, and in 2021, the number is expected to rise to over 2.14 billion.</p>



<p>That’s a huge pool of potential buyers.</p>



<p>So, if you’re not already selling online, these numbers should convince you to do so.</p>



<p>But with more people shopping online, more online businesses are emerging, creating a fierce and competitive marketplace.</p>



<p>This makes it harder for online businesses to stand out from competitors, and the need for new creative ways to promote your product rises.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Takeaway</strong></h3>



<p>You can’t market to everyone, so it’s important to understand your target buyer to know what makes them tick. Personalize your marketing efforts to the individual and you’ll have a much better chance of surviving in the face of competition.</p>
</div></div>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<h3 id="2"><strong>2. Men Spend 68 Percent More Online Than Women (</strong><a href="https://assets.kpmg.com/content/dam/kpmg/xx/pdf/2017/01/the-truth-about-online-consumers.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><strong>KPMG</strong></a><strong>)</strong></h3>



<p>I was shocked when I first read that statistic, but when you think about it, it makes sense.</p>



<p>On average, men spend $220 per transaction compared to $151 per transaction for women. So it’s not that men shop more than women—it’s that they spend <em>more</em> per transaction.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Male consumers are more likely to buy higher-priced items such as grooming products and electronics. Women, by contrast, tend to buy lower-priced items such as cosmetics and skincare products. Moreover, when men shop online, they tend to be efficient, meaning they bulk buy to save time.</p>



<p>So, when selling to a male audience, you can boost conversions by offering <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/product-recommendations" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">related products</a> and package deals.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Here’s an example from <a href="https://www.harrys.com/en/us" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Harry’s</a>:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="613" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image7-26-1024x613.png" alt="Addition For Shave Routine" class="wp-image-90911" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image7-26-1024x613.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image7-26-300x180.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image7-26-768x460.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image7-26-380x227.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image7-26-600x359.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image7-26-760x455.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image7-26-58x35.png 58w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image7-26-84x50.png 84w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image7-26-740x443.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image7-26-220x132.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image7-26-385x230.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image7-26.png 1034w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>When prospects go through Harry’s <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/checkout-optimization" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">checkout</a>, they can add products that compliment their order such as a razor stand or post-shave balm.</p>



<p>Offering related products during checkout makes it easy for customers—both men and women—to quickly add items without having to abandon their cart to search for more products.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Takeaway</strong></h3>



<p>Only show items that are relevant to what’s already in the cart. If the related items go well with the item(s) in the cart, prospects are more likely to buy them too.</p>
</div></div>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<h3 id="3"><strong>3. Generation X Shop More Online Than Baby Boomers and Millennials (</strong><a href="https://assets.kpmg.com/content/dam/kpmg/xx/pdf/2017/01/the-truth-about-online-consumers.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><strong>KPMG</strong></a><strong>)</strong></h3>



<p>People born between 1966-1981, or “Generation Xers,” make more online purchases than any other age group, averaging nearly 19 transactions per year.</p>



<p>This might come as a surprise to many considering Millennials are the digital natives of our society.</p>



<p>However, as Millennials grow older and enter the workforce and start families, their spending increases. It’s expected that Millennials’ online shopping will increase exponentially in the future and far surpass online spending by older generations.&nbsp;</p>



<p>So, if you want to market your products to Millennials, you need to create a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-value-proposition" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">value proposition</a> they can identify with. Millennials view the products they buy as an extension of their image, and if a product doesn’t have a positive effect on their desired self-image, they won’t buy it.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Takeaway</strong></h3>



<p>You need to sell Millennials on a story. Ask yourself, “What is the scenario in which your product will help them overcome a problem or make them feel better?”</p>
</div></div>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<h2><strong>Part 2: Payment and Spending</strong></h2>



<h3 id="4"><strong>4. In 2019, E-Commerce Sales Accounted for 14.1 Percent of All Retail Sales Worldwide (</strong><a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/534123/e-commerce-share-of-retail-sales-worldwide/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><strong>Statista</strong></a><strong>)</strong></h3>



<p>Considering that more than a tenth of all retail sales are made online, you can’t underestimate the importance of continuously optimizing your online store.</p>



<p>Online shopping is becoming more popular than ever, and by 2021, e-commerce sales are expected to reach <a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/534123/e-commerce-share-of-retail-sales-worldwide/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">17.5 percent of retail sales worldwide</a>.</p>



<p>This means there’s more potential for e-tailers to increase traffic and conversions—and a chance to create a better online experience (an area most online stores fall short).</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Takeaway&nbsp;</strong></h3>



<p>Prioritize user experience above all. A compelling value proposition is worth nothing if visitors have a bad experience on your site. This is especially important when it comes to your checkout flow.</p>
</div></div>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<h2 id="5"><strong>5. There Are More Than 286 Million Active PayPal Accounts in The World (</strong><a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/218493/paypals-total-active-registered-accounts-from-2010/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><strong>Statista</strong></a><strong>)</strong></h2>



<p>This is a 17 percent year-on-year growth compared to 220 million in 2017.</p>



<p>With <a href="https://www.paypal.com/us/home" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">PayPal</a>, prospects can buy products online without having to pull out their credit card, simplifying the checkout process further.</p>



<p>The quicker and easier a prospect can go through your checkout, the more likely they are to complete their purchase.</p>



<p>But this doesn’t mean credit card payments are dead. According to one report, <a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/508988/preferred-payment-methods-of-online-shoppers-worldwide/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">42 percent of online shoppers</a> prefer to pay with their credit cards.</p>



<p>Bottom line? Giving visitors multiple payment options will increase conversion rates, and <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/cart-abandonment-strategy" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">reduce cart abandonment</a>.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Takeaway</strong></h3>



<p>Survey your customers to determine their preferred payment options. The more relevant the options you offer, the more money you stand to make.</p>
</div></div>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<h2 id="6"><strong>6. As of Q1 2019, 2.72 Percent of E-Commerce Website Visits Converted into Purchases (<a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/439576/online-shopper-conversion-rate-worldwide/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Statista</a>)</strong></h2>



<p>With an average conversion rate of only 2.72 percent, there’s much room for improvement for e-commerce.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Converting visitors into customers is getting harder because of the fierce competition online.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Much to the chagrin of many business owners, offering low prices or the best products is no longer enough. You need to offer a personal shopping experience for the individual visitor.</p>



<p>Here’s an example from <a href="https://www.asos.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">ASOS</a>, who recognizes returning visitors:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="836" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image11-1-1024x836.jpg" alt="Asos Personalization" class="wp-image-90927" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image11-1-1024x836.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image11-1-300x245.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image11-1-768x627.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image11-1-380x310.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image11-1-600x490.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image11-1-760x621.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image11-1-43x35.jpg 43w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image11-1-61x50.jpg 61w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image11-1-220x180.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image11-1-385x314.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image11-1.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>I’ve shopped with ASOS many times, and because of the cookies ASOS use, I don’t have to log in every time I visit their site.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Takeaway</strong></h3>



<p>Use your cookie settings to recognize returning customers and make it easy for them to buy again. You should also<strong> </strong><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/how-to-use-sleeknote" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">create campaigns</a> that target specific visitor segments that haven’t bought from you before. The more <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/personalized-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">personalized</a> your campaigns are, the more likely they’ll become a customer or at least, an email lead.</p>
</div></div>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<h2 id="7"><strong>7. In Q1 2019, Smartphones Accounted for 65 Percent of Retail Site Visits Worldwide (<a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/568684/e-commerce-website-visit-and-orders-by-device/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Statista</a>)</strong></h2>



<p><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/mobile-commerce-statistics" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Mobile commerce</a> is slowly gaining up on desktop.</p>



<p>It’s now the preferred device for browsing online, with desktop accounting for only 30 percent of online retail visits.</p>



<p>But desktop is still the go-to device when it comes to completing orders.</p>



<p>Mobile accounts for 46 percent of online orders, compared to 54 percent for desktop.</p>



<p>This creates a challenge for e-commerce:</p>



<p><em>The purchase path is no longer straightforward.&nbsp;</em></p>



<p>Consumers jump between channels and devices and their purchase habits are sporadic.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Potential customers will leave items in their cart on mobile and when they return to their cart on desktop—the items are gone.&nbsp;</p>



<p>With that in mind, you need to consider the user journey across devices if you want to optimize conversions.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Takeaway</strong></h3>



<p>Integrate an omnichannel marketing strategy with real-time information across all channels and devices. This means updating information in real-time, so users can access their cart on any device and immediately check out and continue shopping. To learn more about how to convert mobile visitors, <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/popup-statistics" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">read this article</a>.</p>
</div></div>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<h2><strong>Part 3: Shopping Habits</strong></h2>



<h3 id="8"><strong>8. Sixty-Five Percent of Consumers Look Up Price Comparisons on Mobile While in a Physical Store (</strong><a href="https://assets.kpmg.com/content/dam/kpmg/xx/pdf/2017/01/the-truth-about-online-consumers.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><strong>KPMG</strong></a><strong>)&nbsp;</strong></h3>



<p>We’ve all done it, haven’t we?</p>



<p>You want to buy something online, but you want to make sure you don’t overpay. So you go online to see if the product is available elsewhere at a lower price.</p>



<p>To avoid prospects abandoning a store online or off, many businesses use <em>price matching</em>.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Here’s an example from <a href="https://www.ebay.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">eBay</a>:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1000" height="554" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-21.png" alt="Ebay Landing Page" class="wp-image-90935" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-21.png 1000w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-21-300x166.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-21-768x425.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-21-380x211.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-21-600x332.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-21-760x421.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-21-63x35.png 63w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-21-90x50.png 90w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-21-740x410.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-21-220x122.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-21-385x213.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></figure></div>



<p>With price matching, you can prevent prospects from buying the product from a competitor because of pricing.</p>



<p>If a consumer is in your physical store, the chances of them going elsewhere to buy a product if you offer price matching are slim.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Takeaway</strong></h3>



<p>If you offer to match competitor prices, you need to make this visible in your store, both online and off. Have it appear on your front page, or as a sign in your physical store for greater visibility.</p>
</div></div>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<h2 id="9"><strong>9. The Number One Reason People Shop Online is Because They Can Shop 24/7 (</strong><a href="https://assets.kpmg.com/content/dam/kpmg/xx/pdf/2017/01/the-truth-about-online-consumers.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><strong>KPMG</strong></a><strong>)&nbsp;</strong></h2>



<p>Fifty-eight percent of consumers shop online due to online opening hours (or lack thereof).</p>



<p>The Internet never closes, making it easy for consumers to buy any product at any time.</p>



<p>Shopping, for many people, has never been more convenient.</p>



<p>But even though your online store doesn’t close, your customer service department does.</p>



<p>To get ahead of potential issues with prospects who can’t get in touch with you during out of office hours, create separate <a href="https://sleeknote.com/connect-with-visitors" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">contact campaigns</a> for opening hours and closing hours. That way, you can tell visitors when to expect a reply if your staff are offline.</p>



<p>Here’s what those two campaigns could look like.</p>



<p>During opening hours:</p>


<div id="campaign-template-block_5f75d4b68bc47" class="block-campaign-template">
    <div class="template-placeholder">
    <img src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image10-23.png" title="Create a similar campaign">        <p class="image-caption">Create a similar campaign</p>
    </div>
    <div class="cta-block">
        <div class="tag">NEW</div>
        <div class="cta-block-content">
            <p>Like what you see? Load this high-converting template in our editor and customize it to the look and feel of your business.</p>
            <a class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" href="https://sleeknote.com/template-signup/?templateId=201805-30-Questions&#038;goalId=contact">Try it out</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>



<p>During closing hours:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="427" height="213" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image1-25.png" alt="Call Us" class="wp-image-90887" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image1-25.png 427w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image1-25-300x150.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image1-25-380x190.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image1-25-70x35.png 70w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image1-25-100x50.png 100w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image1-25-220x110.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image1-25-385x192.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 427px) 100vw, 427px" /></figure></div>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Takeaway</strong></h3>



<p>Schedule campaigns in advance to activate and deactivate on schedule. When you let prospects know when they can expect an answer they’ll be more patient with you (and more likely to buy).</p>
</div></div>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<h2 id="10"><strong>10. Thirty Percent of Consumers Say The Would Rather Buy from a Website They’ve Bought from Previously (</strong><a href="https://assets.kpmg.com/content/dam/kpmg/xx/pdf/2017/01/the-truth-about-online-consumers.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><strong>KPMG</strong></a><strong>)&nbsp;</strong></h2>



<p>We’re creatures of habit. When it comes to buying online, we rely on our own and other’s experiences to influence our purchasing decisions.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Once consumers have had a good experience with a brand, they’re more likely to return to that brand and even recommend it to others.</p>



<p>That’s why you should try to get new customers to sign up for your <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/customer-loyalty-programs" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">loyalty program</a> or your newsletter. Then you can reach out to them via <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-email-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">email marketing</a> and turn them into repeat buyers.</p>



<p>The best time to ask customers to do so is on your <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/thank-you-page" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">thank you page</a> after they’ve bought from you.</p>



<p>Here’s an example of how you can ask new customers to join your loyalty club:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="734" height="506" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image14-20.png" alt="Want To Save Your Receipt" class="wp-image-90939" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image14-20.png 734w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image14-20-300x207.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image14-20-380x262.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image14-20-600x414.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image14-20-51x35.png 51w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image14-20-73x50.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image14-20-711x490.png 711w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image14-20-220x152.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image14-20-385x265.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 734px) 100vw, 734px" /></figure></div>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Takeaway&nbsp;</strong></h3>



<p>Consider where your customers are in the buyer&#8217;s journey. If they just bought something, they might not respond well to a sales email the next day. But if you target them over time with relevant offers based on their purchase history, they’ll most likely return to your store again.</p>
</div></div>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<h2 id="11"><strong>11. Fifty-Nine Percent of 16-36 Year-Olds Head to Amazon Before Any Other E-Commerce Website (</strong><a href="https://whatmillennialswant.inviqa.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><strong>Inviqa</strong></a><strong>)</strong></h2>



<p>I think we can all agree that <a href="https://www.amazon.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Amazon</a> is a top contender in the e-commerce market.</p>



<p>Again, it comes down to convenience. If a prospect can buy all the different items they need in the same place, then it’s a no-brainer.</p>



<p>So, to accommodate this growing trend, consider selling on Amazon, if your country permits.</p>



<p>You can even add a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/call-to-action" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">call-to-action</a> button on your site that links to the item on Amazon.</p>



<p>Here’s an example from <a href="http://breakthroughclothing.in/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Breakthrough Clothing</a>:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="613" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image4-25-1024x613.png" alt="Product Page" class="wp-image-90899" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image4-25-1024x613.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image4-25-300x180.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image4-25-768x460.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image4-25-380x227.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image4-25-600x359.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image4-25-760x455.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image4-25-58x35.png 58w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image4-25-84x50.png 84w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image4-25-740x443.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image4-25-220x132.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image4-25-385x230.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image4-25.png 1328w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Takeaway</strong></h3>



<p>To sell your products on Amazon, make the journey from your product page to the corresponding product page on Amazon as seamless as possible.</p>
</div></div>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<h2><strong>Part 4: Cart Abandonment</strong></h2>



<h3 id="12"><strong>12. Fifty-Three Percent of Online Shoppers Abandon Their Carts Because of Unexpected Extra Costs (</strong><a href="https://baymard.com/lists/cart-abandonment-rate" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><strong>Baymard Institute</strong></a><strong>)</strong></h3>



<p>“Unexpected extra costs” include, tax, fees, and of course, shipping.</p>



<p>To avoid shoppers abandoning their carts, then, make visitors aware of any extra costs upfront before they enter the checkout. You can also offer free shipping on orders above a specific value to <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/cart-abandonment-popup-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">reduce cart abandonment</a> and increase average order value.</p>



<p>According to HubSpot, <a href="http://cdn2.hubspot.net/hub/310840/file-2031207983-pdf/VWO_ecommerce_report_new.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">24 percent of shoppers</a> are ready to spend more to qualify for free shipping, so this is a great way to increase the average order value.<br><br>Whenever a visitor adds an item to their cart, track the basket value and trigger a campaign in the first step of your cart. Then, if the order value isn’t high enough, offer free shipping.<br><br>To encourage visitors to buy more, you could <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/product-recommendation-popups" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">add product recommendations in your campaign</a> with an “add to cart” call-to-action.<br><br>Here’s an example:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="694" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cross-Sell-Products-1024x694.jpg" alt="Cross-Sell Products" class="wp-image-90871" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cross-Sell-Products-1024x694.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cross-Sell-Products-300x203.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cross-Sell-Products-768x520.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cross-Sell-Products-380x257.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cross-Sell-Products-600x407.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cross-Sell-Products-760x515.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cross-Sell-Products-52x35.jpg 52w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cross-Sell-Products-74x50.jpg 74w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cross-Sell-Products-723x490.jpg 723w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cross-Sell-Products-220x149.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cross-Sell-Products-385x261.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cross-Sell-Products.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Takeaway</strong></h3>



<p>Identify the reasons shoppers abandon checkout and address those reasons with an <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/exit-intent" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">exit-intent</a> campaign or with an <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/abandoned-cart-emails" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">abandoned cart email</a>.<br></p>
</div></div>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<h2 id="13"><strong>13. Abandoned Cart Emails Have an Average Open Rate of 45 Percent (</strong><a href="https://moosend.com/blog/cart-abandonment-stats/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><strong>Moosend</strong></a><strong>)</strong></h2>



<p>If you’ve ever given up checking out before completing an order you&#8217;ve likely received an abandoned cart email.&nbsp;</p>



<p>And if you have, you know that its goal is to help you overcome objections and buy something.&nbsp;</p>



<p>The average revenue per abandoned cart email is <a href="https://www.bigcommerce.com/blog/abandoned-carts/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">$5.64</a>, compared to only $0.02 for promotional emails, and $0.18 per welcome email you send.</p>



<p>So, there’s a lot of money to be made here.</p>



<p>Here’s a good example from <a href="https://www.mancrates.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Man Crates</a>:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="855" height="534" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image18-18.png" alt="Man Crates" class="wp-image-90955" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image18-18.png 855w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image18-18-300x187.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image18-18-768x480.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image18-18-380x237.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image18-18-600x375.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image18-18-760x475.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image18-18-56x35.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image18-18-80x50.png 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image18-18-740x462.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image18-18-220x137.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image18-18-385x240.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 855px) 100vw, 855px" /></figure></div>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Takeaway</strong></h3>



<p>There’s a reason we add items to our cart—and a reason, or reasons, why we chose not to buy. If you can identify these two reasons with your prospects, you’re already well on your way to writing the perfect recovery email.</p>
</div></div>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<h3 id="14"><strong>14. Abandoned Cart Emails Sent within 20 Minutes Have an Average Conversion rate of 5.2 Percent (</strong><a href="https://www.prestashop.com/en/blog/recovery-of-abandoned-carts-tips-advices" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><strong>PrestaShop</strong></a><strong>)</strong></h3>



<p>Your abandoned cart emails’ timing has a great effect on conversion rates.</p>



<p>Emails sent within an hour have an average conversion rate of <a href="https://www.prestashop.com/en/blog/recovery-of-abandoned-carts-tips-advices" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">4.5 percent</a>, while emails sent more than 24 hours after cart abandonment only convert at around 2.6 percent.</p>



<p>Consumers are constantly bombarded with promotional material, and that makes it harder for marketers to stay top of mind with prospects.</p>



<p>That’s why it’s so important to send abandoned cart emails directly after a prospect abandons their cart, to ensure your brand is still top of mind when they receive the email.</p>



<p>Here’s an example from <a href="https://beanbox.co/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Bean Box</a>:&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="656" height="724" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image9-25.png" alt="Bean Box" class="wp-image-90919" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image9-25.png 656w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image9-25-272x300.png 272w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image9-25-380x419.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image9-25-600x662.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image9-25-32x35.png 32w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image9-25-45x50.png 45w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image9-25-444x490.png 444w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image9-25-220x243.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image9-25-385x425.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 656px) 100vw, 656px" /></figure></div>



<p>This email arrived only ten minutes after I abandoned my cart and while I was still thinking about coffee.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Takeaway</strong></h3>



<p>Automate your abandoned cart emails and trigger them to go out within 20-minutes after a prospect abandons their cart. Make sure to write a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/cart-abandonment-subject-lines" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">compelling subject line</a> and include the cart items in the email along with multiple calls-to-action to go back to the cart.</p>
</div></div>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<h3 id="15"><strong>15. Exit-Intent Campaigns Convert Between 2-4 Percent of Abandoning Visitors (Sleeknote)</strong></h3>



<p>I know what you’re thinking.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Yes, <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/exit-intent" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">exit-intent campaigns</a> are annoying&#8230;&nbsp;</p>



<p>But only if you misuse them.</p>



<p>One good practice is adding exit-intent campaigns to your checkout to reduce cart abandonment. With exit-intent campaigns, you can turn abandoning visitors into email leads or even better, get them to complete their purchase.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Here’s an example from <a href="https://minimumfashion.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">minimum</a> that focuses on getting leads:&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="616" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-1024x616.jpg" alt="Finish Your Order Popup" class="wp-image-90915" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-1024x616.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-300x181.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-768x462.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-380x229.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-600x361.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-760x457.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-58x35.jpg 58w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-83x50.jpg 83w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-740x445.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-220x132.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-385x232.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>This specific campaign had a conversion rate of <strong>37.4 percent</strong> when it was live.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Another option is to give the <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/discount-strategy" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">discount code</a> directly in the campaign like <a href="https://nicehair.dk/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Nicehair</a>:&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="789" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-1024x789.jpg" alt="Stop" class="wp-image-90947" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-1024x789.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-300x231.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-768x592.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-380x293.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-600x463.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-760x586.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-45x35.jpg 45w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-65x50.jpg 65w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-636x490.jpg 636w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-220x170.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-385x297.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Nicehair tested this campaign on their different sites (International site, Danish site, Swedish site, and Norwegian site) for a limited time to see if they could reduce cart abandonment.&nbsp;</p>



<p>They made clear that the discount code needed to be used immediately, encouraging abandoning shoppers to follow through with their purchase.&nbsp;</p>



<p>The average conversion rate of this campaign across all four sites? An amazing <strong>44.76 percent</strong>. That’s right: almost half the visitors who were about to abandon their cart returned to it after seeing this campaign.&nbsp;</p>



<p>But even though these two campaigns performed so well, Nicehair and minimum know the importance of using discounts sparingly.&nbsp;</p>



<p>When you don’t use discounts often, you can get away with offering smaller discounts and still have great success with your campaign.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Takeaway&nbsp;</strong></h3>



<p>Identify why visitors abandon their cart and try to eliminate that concern in your exit-intent campaigns. Use discounts sparingly and think about what other value you can give to abandoning shoppers. (For instance, offer to save cart, notify when items go on sale, invite them to get in touch with potential questions, and so on).</p>
</div></div>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<h2><strong>Part 5: Reviews and Customer Service</strong></h2>



<h3 id="16"><strong>16. Thirty Percent of Online Consumers Have Posted Product Feedback Online (<a href="https://assets.kpmg.com/content/dam/kpmg/xx/pdf/2017/01/the-truth-about-online-consumers.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">KPMG</a>)</strong></h3>



<p>Reviews are highly effective when it comes to nudging prospects to make a purchase, and that’s why you should always encourage your visitors to review their shopping experience.</p>



<p>The best time to ask for a review is right after a purchase on your thank you page.</p>



<p>Here’s an example from <a href="https://www.livingshop.dk/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Livingshop</a>:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="733" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-2-1024x733.jpg" alt="Help Us To Improve" class="wp-image-90891" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-2-1024x733.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-2-300x215.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-2-768x550.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-2-380x272.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-2-600x430.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-2-760x544.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-2-49x35.jpg 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-2-70x50.jpg 70w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-2-684x490.jpg 684w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-2-220x158.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-2-385x276.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-2.jpg 1036w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>If customers don’t respond to the above, you should follow up with an email, like <a href="https://billigvoks.dk/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Billigvoks</a>:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="638" height="747" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image15-22.png" alt="Write A Review" class="wp-image-90943" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image15-22.png 638w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image15-22-256x300.png 256w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image15-22-380x445.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image15-22-600x703.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image15-22-30x35.png 30w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image15-22-43x50.png 43w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image15-22-419x490.png 419w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image15-22-220x258.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image15-22-385x451.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 638px) 100vw, 638px" /></figure></div>



<p>If your customers have reviewed your business on review sites such as Trustpilot, you need to include some of these reviews on your website.</p>



<p>It’s not just enough to have them on third-party sites if you want them to be effective—they have to be where the action happens, which is on your website.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Takeaway</strong></h3>



<p>Encourage customers to leave reviews and showcase them on your website. If you have a review section on your product pages, you need to include your bad reviews too. Otherwise, any good reviews will seem untrustworthy.</p>
</div></div>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<h2 id="17"><strong>17. Eighty-One Percent of Consumers Trust the Advice of Family and Friends Over Businesses (</strong><a href="https://research.hubspot.com/customer-acquisition-study" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><strong>HubSpot</strong></a><strong>)</strong></h2>



<p>Online shopping has made it easy for consumers to show a specific product to their friends or family to get a second opinion before making a purchase.&nbsp;</p>



<p>This can be shared through a link on SMS, email, social media, and other channels.&nbsp;</p>



<p>If friends and family recommend one product over the other, we are more likely to choose the recommended one, regardless of price and quality.&nbsp;</p>



<p>To help encourage visitors to buy, include different sharing options that will help potential customers get a thumbs up from their friends.</p>



<p>You can also do as <a href="https://www.mulberry.com/gb/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Mulberry</a> and include a “Hint hint” option on product pages:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="588" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image5-1024x588.jpg" alt="Mulberry Hint" class="wp-image-90903" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image5-1024x588.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image5-300x172.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image5-768x441.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image5-380x218.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image5-600x345.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image5-760x436.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image5-61x35.jpg 61w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image5-87x50.jpg 87w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image5-740x425.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image5-220x126.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image5-385x221.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image5.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>When you click the button, this popup triggers, giving you the option to email a friend to inform them you like this product.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="835" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12-1024x835.jpg" alt="Hint Hint" class="wp-image-90931" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12-1024x835.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12-300x245.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12-768x627.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12-380x310.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12-600x490.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12-760x620.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12-43x35.jpg 43w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12-61x50.jpg 61w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12-601x490.jpg 601w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12-220x179.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12-385x314.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Here’s what the email looks like:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="521" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image6-2-521x1024.jpg" alt="Phone Clutch" class="wp-image-90907" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image6-2-521x1024.jpg 521w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image6-2-153x300.jpg 153w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image6-2-768x1510.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image6-2-781x1536.jpg 781w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image6-2-380x747.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image6-2-600x1179.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image6-2-760x1494.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image6-2-18x35.jpg 18w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image6-2-25x50.jpg 25w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image6-2-249x490.jpg 249w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image6-2-220x432.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image6-2-385x757.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image6-2.jpg 1017w" sizes="(max-width: 521px) 100vw, 521px" /></figure></div>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Takeaway</strong></h3>



<p>Make it easy for consumers to share products from your site with friends and family through different channels. Make sure to include a direct link to the product along with an <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/visual-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">image of the product</a>.</p>
</div></div>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<h2 id="18"><strong>18. Eighty Percent of Respondents Said They Had Stopped Doing Business with a Company Because of Poor Customer Experience (</strong><a href="https://research.hubspot.com/customer-acquisition-study" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><strong>HubSpot</strong></a><strong>)</strong></h2>



<p>Someone once said never underestimate the power of a smile. (Or maybe it was me, I can’t remember.)</p>



<p>While we might not be able to smile to our online customers, we can make them feel appreciated by being positive and giving them a unique experience when they get in touch with us.</p>



<p>A negative experience will stay with prospects longer than a positive experience.</p>



<p>That’s why you need to ensure that every person who interacts with your brand has a good experience.</p>



<p>A good idea is to survey your site visitors to get insights on how to improve the customer experience on your site—even if you think it’s good already.&nbsp;</p>



<p>One way to do that is to use a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/features/multistep" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">multistep campaign</a> on your site to politely ask for visitor feedback.</p>



<p>Here’s an example of what that could look like:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="765" height="461" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image19-16.png" alt="Help Us Improve Popup Examples" class="wp-image-90959" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image19-16.png 765w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image19-16-300x181.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image19-16-380x229.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image19-16-600x362.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image19-16-760x458.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image19-16-58x35.png 58w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image19-16-83x50.png 83w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image19-16-740x446.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image19-16-220x133.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image19-16-385x232.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 765px) 100vw, 765px" /></figure></div>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Takeaway</strong></h3>



<p>Survey visitors and ask about their experience. The more information you have, the better you can prevent negative experiences.</p>
</div></div>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<h2 id="19"><strong>19. Fifty-One Percent of Consumers Trust Companies Who Make It Easy for Visitors to Contact the People behind the Company (</strong><a href="https://assets.kpmg.com/content/dam/kpmg/xx/pdf/2017/01/the-truth-about-online-consumers.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><strong>KPMG</strong></a><strong>)</strong></h2>



<p>How many times have you wanted to get in touch with a business and not been able to find any contact information?</p>



<p>More than once, right?</p>



<p>It’s not a good user experience.&nbsp;</p>



<p>You need to make it easy for people to get in touch with you. Imagine if a potential customer can’t get in touch with you and they then decide to shop elsewhere.</p>



<p>To prevent this, you can add a contact campaign to your site inviting visitors to get in touch with you.</p>



<p>Here’s what that could look like:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="679" height="403" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image3-24.png" alt="Hi I am Patric Popup" class="wp-image-90895" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image3-24.png 679w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image3-24-300x178.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image3-24-380x226.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image3-24-600x356.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image3-24-59x35.png 59w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image3-24-84x50.png 84w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image3-24-220x131.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image3-24-385x229.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 679px) 100vw, 679px" /></figure></div>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Takeaway</strong></h3>



<p>Invite visitors to get in touch so you can answer any questions or concerns they might have. Make your contact forms personal by adding photos of your staff, and customize campaigns to different pages on your site.</p>
</div></div>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>






