<p><a href="#Follow-Up-with-Event-Attendees">9. Follow Up with Event Attendees</a></p>



<h2><strong>How and When to Use Discounts</strong></h2>



<p>Discounts aren’t for everyone.<br></p>



<p>And I can’t tell you if you should use them or not. But I can tell you <em>how</em> to use them.<br></p>



<p>There are countless ways to use discounts to get more leads and sales for your online store.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>But you need to use them wisely.<br></p>



<p>Your discounting strategy should always depend on your business goals and the individual visitor. Maybe you want to discount discontinued items to clear out inventory and not to increase revenue.<br></p>



<p>Let’s have a look at how and when to use discounts, and what the alternatives could be.<br></p>



<h2 id="Nudge-New-Visitors-with-a-Special-Offer"><strong>1. Nudge New Visitors with a Special Offer</strong></h2>



<p>When a visitor first enters your site, they might not be ready to buy.<br></p>



<p>So offering them a discount code to use right away, isn’t always the best strategy.<br></p>



<p>Instead of asking new visitors to buy this early into <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/the-buyers-journey" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">the buyer’s journey</a>, you should ask them for a smaller commitment—like giving you their email address in exchange for a discount code.<br></p>



<p>Here’s what that might look like:</p>







<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="797" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/New-Visitor-Discount-1024x797.jpg" alt="New Visitor Discount" class="wp-image-75409" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/New-Visitor-Discount-1024x797.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/New-Visitor-Discount-300x234.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/New-Visitor-Discount-768x598.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/New-Visitor-Discount-380x296.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/New-Visitor-Discount-600x467.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/New-Visitor-Discount-760x592.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/New-Visitor-Discount-45x35.jpg 45w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/New-Visitor-Discount-64x50.jpg 64w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/New-Visitor-Discount-630x490.jpg 630w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/New-Visitor-Discount-220x171.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/New-Visitor-Discount-385x300.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/New-Visitor-Discount.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>When creating a campaign for new visitors, it’s important to:<br></p>



<ul><li><strong>Target a specific visitor segment: </strong>To ensure you only offer this discount to new site visitors, place a cookie in new visitors’ browsers. Doing so allows you to track new visitors vs. returning visitors and hide or show campaigns to this segment.</li><li><strong>Personalize the copy: </strong>Make sure your target segment know the offer is exclusive to them. This makes the message and offer more relevant which will increase conversions.</li><li><strong>Give people a reason for your discount:</strong> If you want people to accept your discount, give them a reason. As Robert Cialdini writes in his book <a href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/006124189X/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)"><em>Influence</em></a>, “People simply like to have reasons for what they do.” The best part is, it works even if the reason is obvious. For instance, it can be as simple as in the example above where visitors get a discount because they’re new visitors. (See: <a href="https://jamesclear.com/copy-machine-study" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">The Copy Machine Study</a>.)</li></ul>



<div class="wp-block-group"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Alternative</strong>: If you don’t want to offer discounts to new visitors, you can try to sell them on the value of your newsletter to get their email address.</p>



<p>Here’s an example from <a href="https://www.perchs.dk/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">A.C. Perchs</a>:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="1024" height="567" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A.C.-Perchs-Newsletter-1-1024x567.jpg" alt="A.C. Perchs Newsletter" class="wp-image-79424" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A.C.-Perchs-Newsletter-1-1024x567.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A.C.-Perchs-Newsletter-1-300x166.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A.C.-Perchs-Newsletter-1-768x426.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A.C.-Perchs-Newsletter-1-380x211.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A.C.-Perchs-Newsletter-1-600x333.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A.C.-Perchs-Newsletter-1-760x421.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A.C.-Perchs-Newsletter-1-63x35.jpg 63w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A.C.-Perchs-Newsletter-1-90x50.jpg 90w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A.C.-Perchs-Newsletter-1-740x410.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A.C.-Perchs-Newsletter-1-220x122.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A.C.-Perchs-Newsletter-1-385x213.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/A.C.-Perchs-Newsletter-1.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>
</div></div>
</div></div>



<h2 id="Reward-Loyal-Customers"><strong>2. Reward Loyal Customers</strong></h2>



<p>If you have a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/customer-loyalty-programs" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">loyalty club</a>, you can, and should, use discounts to reward loyal customers.<br></p>



<p>For example, when a customer spends a certain amount on your site, you can offer them a discount code on their next order as a thank you.<br></p>



<p><a href="https://www.loyalty.com/home/insights/article-details/cx-intention-vs.-impact-making-sense-of-the-ever-evolving-retail" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">One report</a> shows that 76% of customers want personalized offers based on their purchase history.<br></p>



<p>So offering rewards based on your members’ previous purchases is a great way to personalize offers.<br></p>



<p>Here’s an example of how <a href="https://www.hm.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">H&amp;M</a> rewards their club members:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="577" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/H_M-Loyalty-Club-Rewards-577x1024.jpg" alt="H_M Loyalty Club Rewards" class="wp-image-75401" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/H_M-Loyalty-Club-Rewards-577x1024.jpg 577w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/H_M-Loyalty-Club-Rewards-169x300.jpg 169w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/H_M-Loyalty-Club-Rewards-380x675.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/H_M-Loyalty-Club-Rewards-20x35.jpg 20w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/H_M-Loyalty-Club-Rewards-28x50.jpg 28w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/H_M-Loyalty-Club-Rewards-276x490.jpg 276w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/H_M-Loyalty-Club-Rewards-220x391.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/H_M-Loyalty-Club-Rewards-385x683.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/H_M-Loyalty-Club-Rewards.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 577px) 100vw, 577px" /></figure></div>



<p>The reward is a 10% discount on all dresses with an expiration date to nudge on-the-fence buyers to take action.<br></p>



<p>It’s worth mentioning that the value of the rewards depends on the number of points you earn. The more points you get, the bigger the rewards—and the more likely you are to buy again.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Alternative</strong>: There’s always an alternative to offering discounts. If you want to reward loyal customers, offer free shipping instead.<br></p>



<p>H&amp;M also offers free shipping to club members:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="1024" height="238" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/H_M-Free-Shipping-1024x238.jpg" alt="H_M Free Shipping" class="wp-image-75397" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/H_M-Free-Shipping-1024x238.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/H_M-Free-Shipping-300x70.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/H_M-Free-Shipping-768x179.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/H_M-Free-Shipping-380x88.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/H_M-Free-Shipping-600x140.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/H_M-Free-Shipping-760x177.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/H_M-Free-Shipping-151x35.jpg 151w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/H_M-Free-Shipping-215x50.jpg 215w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/H_M-Free-Shipping-740x172.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/H_M-Free-Shipping-220x51.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/H_M-Free-Shipping-385x90.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/H_M-Free-Shipping.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>
</div></div>



<h2 id="Increase-Sales-During-Holidays"><strong>3. Increase Sales During Holidays</strong></h2>



<p>During specific holidays, many consumers go online to shop for gifts due to an increase in holiday promotions.<br></p>



<p>So, why not capitalize on the increased traffic during holidays and <a href="https://sleeknote.com/guide-your-visitors" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">guide your visitors</a> to relevant offers?<br></p>



<p>Here’s an example of a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/black-friday-marketing-strategies" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Black Friday</a> campaign from <a rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" href="https://www.realcoffee.com/" target="_blank">Real Coffee</a>:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="659" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Real-Coffee-Black-Friday-Campaign-1024x659.jpg" alt="Real Coffee Black Friday Campaign" class="wp-image-75421" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Real-Coffee-Black-Friday-Campaign-1024x659.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Real-Coffee-Black-Friday-Campaign-300x193.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Real-Coffee-Black-Friday-Campaign-768x494.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Real-Coffee-Black-Friday-Campaign-380x244.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Real-Coffee-Black-Friday-Campaign-600x386.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Real-Coffee-Black-Friday-Campaign-760x489.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Real-Coffee-Black-Friday-Campaign-54x35.jpg 54w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Real-Coffee-Black-Friday-Campaign-78x50.jpg 78w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Real-Coffee-Black-Friday-Campaign-740x476.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Real-Coffee-Black-Friday-Campaign-220x142.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Real-Coffee-Black-Friday-Campaign-385x248.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Real-Coffee-Black-Friday-Campaign.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>The campaign showed on all pages on the website during Black Friday, except for the actual page with the offers.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>That means when you click the campaign, you go directly to a landing page with all the available Black Friday offers.<br></p>



<p>The page only had Black Friday offers, making it easier for prospects to go through the selection of discounted products and make a decision on which to get.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Alternative</strong>: Not all businesses need to offer discounts during holidays to get more sales (far from it). You can also use <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/content-upgrades" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">content upgrades</a> to inspire sales (even if you don’t have a blog). For example, you can offer inspiration for creative dates on Valentine’s Day, free recipes for Thanksgiving, free DIY guides for Christmas decorations, etc.<br></p>



<p>Offer product recommendations in your free guides and visitors will be more likely to buy from you during the holidays.</p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="Use-Early-Bird-Discounts-for-New-Products"><strong>4. Use Early-Bird Discounts for New Products</strong></h2>



<p>When you launch a new product, you want as many people to buy it as possible, right?<br></p>



<p>Many online stores promote a pre-order discount on upcoming products for this very reason.<br></p>



<p>Here’s a good recent example from <a href="https://redroostercoffee.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Red Rooster Coffee Roaster</a>:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="661" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Red-Rooster-Earlybird-Discount-Email-661x1024.jpg" alt="Red Rooster Earlybird Discount Email" class="wp-image-75425" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Red-Rooster-Earlybird-Discount-Email-661x1024.jpg 661w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Red-Rooster-Earlybird-Discount-Email-194x300.jpg 194w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Red-Rooster-Earlybird-Discount-Email-768x1190.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Red-Rooster-Earlybird-Discount-Email-380x589.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Red-Rooster-Earlybird-Discount-Email-600x930.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Red-Rooster-Earlybird-Discount-Email-760x1178.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Red-Rooster-Earlybird-Discount-Email-23x35.jpg 23w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Red-Rooster-Earlybird-Discount-Email-32x50.jpg 32w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Red-Rooster-Earlybird-Discount-Email-316x490.jpg 316w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Red-Rooster-Earlybird-Discount-Email-220x341.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Red-Rooster-Earlybird-Discount-Email-385x597.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Red-Rooster-Earlybird-Discount-Email.jpg 800w" sizes="(max-width: 661px) 100vw, 661px" /></figure></div>



<p>They added <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/scarcity-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">scarcity</a> to the email by limiting the discount to the first 30 orders.<br></p>



<p>By doing so, they make the offer seem more exclusive which drives more traffic to the new product.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>It’s important to mention here that you need to be careful when offering discounts on new products.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Discounting a product before it’s launched can devalue it in the prospect’s mind.<br></p>



<p>So don’t offer large discounts on new products, and make sure that the discount is only a small percentage of the full price of the product.<br></p>



<p>For example, the price of the coffee from Red Rooster Coffee Roaster is $25.99, so that’s about a 20% discount.<br></p>



<p>When you discount your products, you need to consider if you want to offer a percentage discount or dollar amounts.<br></p>



<p>As a rule of thumb, <strong>you should go with the option that has the highest perceived value.</strong><br></p>



<p>So, taking the above example, I would go with the 20% discount because it seems higher than the $5 discount, even though the savings are the same no matter what you choose.<br></p>



<p>Again, it’s a balance, and it might be worth testing which type of discount works best for your audience and the product you’re discounting.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Alternative:</strong> In many cases, it’s enough to use scarcity to get people to pre-order items without a discount. A good strategy is “The few-items-left-tactic” where you add how many items are available to pre-order.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>In his book, <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Theory-Psychological-Reactance-Jack-Brehm/dp/0121298507" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)"><em>Theory of Psychological Reactance</em></a>, Jack Brehm states that when opportunities become less available we lose our freedom of choice. And when our choices are limited or threatened, our need to keep that freedom makes us want the item even more than before. It’s simple psychology.<br></p>



<p>Here’s an example from <a href="https://www.deathwishcoffee.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Death Wish Coffee</a>:&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="422" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Death-Wish-Coffee-Email-1024x422.jpg" alt="Death Wish Coffee Email" class="wp-image-75365" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Death-Wish-Coffee-Email-1024x422.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Death-Wish-Coffee-Email-300x124.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Death-Wish-Coffee-Email-768x316.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Death-Wish-Coffee-Email-380x156.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Death-Wish-Coffee-Email-600x247.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Death-Wish-Coffee-Email-760x313.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Death-Wish-Coffee-Email-85x35.jpg 85w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Death-Wish-Coffee-Email-121x50.jpg 121w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Death-Wish-Coffee-Email-740x305.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Death-Wish-Coffee-Email-220x91.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Death-Wish-Coffee-Email-385x158.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Death-Wish-Coffee-Email.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>
</div></div>



<h2 id="Reduce-Abandoned-Carts"><strong>5. Reduce Abandoned Carts</strong></h2>



<p>It&#8217;s likely you already use this strategy, but I&#8217;d be remiss if I didn&#8217;t mention it.<br></p>



<p><a href="https://baymard.com/lists/cart-abandonment-rate" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Sixty percent of online shoppers</a> abandon their carts because of unexpected extra costs so by offering a discount to abandoning shoppers, you can recover some of that lost revenue.<br></p>



<p>Here’s how <a href="https://nicehair.dk/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Nicehair</a> uses <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/exit-intent" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">exit-intent campaigns</a> to reduce cart abandonment:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="789" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Nicehair-Exit-Intent-1024x789.jpg" alt="Nicehair Exit-Intent" class="wp-image-75413" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Nicehair-Exit-Intent-1024x789.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Nicehair-Exit-Intent-300x231.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Nicehair-Exit-Intent-768x592.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Nicehair-Exit-Intent-380x293.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Nicehair-Exit-Intent-600x463.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Nicehair-Exit-Intent-760x586.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Nicehair-Exit-Intent-45x35.jpg 45w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Nicehair-Exit-Intent-65x50.jpg 65w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Nicehair-Exit-Intent-636x490.jpg 636w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Nicehair-Exit-Intent-220x170.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Nicehair-Exit-Intent-385x297.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Nicehair-Exit-Intent.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>It’s important to mention that you should use discounts in your cart sparingly. If you constantly offer a discount on exit-intent in your cart, visitors will come to expect it and abandon just to get a discount and not pay full price.<br></p>



<p>Nicehair ran this campaign as an experiment for a limited amount of time, and their overall <strong>conversion rate was 44.76%</strong>. That’s almost half of abandoning visitors who returned to their cart.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Alternative</strong>: An alternative to offering discounts in your cart is to offer free shipping on orders with an average order value above a certain amount.<br></p>



<p>According to HubSpot, <a href="http://cdn2.hubspot.net/hub/310840/file-2031207983-pdf/VWO_ecommerce_report_new.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">24% of shoppers</a> are ready to spend more to qualify for free shipping, so this is a great way to increase the average order value.<br></p>



<p>Here’s how you can ask abandoning visitors to add items to their cart using <a href="https://sleeknote.com/collect-email-addresses" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Sleeknote</a>:<br></p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="1024" height="630" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Free-Shipping-Exit-Intent-Template-600x369@2x-1024x630.jpg" alt="Free Shipping Exit-Intent" class="wp-image-103201" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Free-Shipping-Exit-Intent-Template-600x369@2x-1024x630.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Free-Shipping-Exit-Intent-Template-600x369@2x-300x185.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Free-Shipping-Exit-Intent-Template-600x369@2x-768x472.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Free-Shipping-Exit-Intent-Template-600x369@2x-380x234.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Free-Shipping-Exit-Intent-Template-600x369@2x-600x369.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Free-Shipping-Exit-Intent-Template-600x369@2x-760x467.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Free-Shipping-Exit-Intent-Template-600x369@2x-57x35.jpg 57w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Free-Shipping-Exit-Intent-Template-600x369@2x-81x50.jpg 81w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Free-Shipping-Exit-Intent-Template-600x369@2x-740x455.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Free-Shipping-Exit-Intent-Template-600x369@2x-220x135.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Free-Shipping-Exit-Intent-Template-600x369@2x-385x237.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Free-Shipping-Exit-Intent-Template-600x369@2x.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>
</div></div>



<h2 id="Reward-Referrals-from-Existing-Customers"><strong>6. Reward Referrals from Existing Customers</strong></h2>



<p>If you’re like most business owners, you know the importance of <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/referral-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">referral marketing</a>.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>The problem, though, is few build a predictable and repeatable referral system into their marketing.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>And the numbers couldn’t be more revealing.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>According to <a href="https://www.referralcandy.com/blog/referral-marketing-awesome-infographic/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">ReferralCandy</a>, 83% of satisfied customers are willing to refer products and services. Yet, only 29% actually do.<br></p>



<p>Discounts, then, are an effective incentive for inviting customers to refer loved ones.<br></p>



<p>Here’s a recent email I got from <a href="https://bonobos.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Bonobos</a>:</p>







<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="465" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bonobos-Refer-a-Friend-465x1024.jpg" alt="Bonobos Refer a Friend" class="wp-image-75361" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bonobos-Refer-a-Friend-465x1024.jpg 465w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bonobos-Refer-a-Friend-136x300.jpg 136w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bonobos-Refer-a-Friend-768x1690.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bonobos-Refer-a-Friend-698x1536.jpg 698w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bonobos-Refer-a-Friend-931x2048.jpg 931w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bonobos-Refer-a-Friend-380x836.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bonobos-Refer-a-Friend-600x1321.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bonobos-Refer-a-Friend-760x1673.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bonobos-Refer-a-Friend-16x35.jpg 16w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bonobos-Refer-a-Friend-23x50.jpg 23w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bonobos-Refer-a-Friend-223x490.jpg 223w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bonobos-Refer-a-Friend-220x484.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bonobos-Refer-a-Friend-385x847.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bonobos-Refer-a-Friend-scaled.jpg 1163w" sizes="(max-width: 465px) 100vw, 465px" /></figure></div>



<p>By offering discounts to both the referrer and the referral, Bonobos incentivize both parties to buy something. Win. Win.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Alternative</strong>: Again, there are alternatives to offering a discount in exchange for referrals. You can offer to send a free gift or a product sample when a customer has referred friends.<br></p>



<p>Here’s an example from Bombas who offers two free pairs of socks for every customer they refer:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="544" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bombas-Referral-Program-1024x544.jpg" alt="Bombas Referral Program" class="wp-image-75357" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bombas-Referral-Program-1024x544.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bombas-Referral-Program-300x160.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bombas-Referral-Program-768x408.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bombas-Referral-Program-380x202.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bombas-Referral-Program-600x319.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bombas-Referral-Program-760x404.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bombas-Referral-Program-66x35.jpg 66w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bombas-Referral-Program-94x50.jpg 94w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bombas-Referral-Program-740x393.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bombas-Referral-Program-220x117.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bombas-Referral-Program-385x205.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bombas-Referral-Program.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Note: You don’t need to add a discount for referrals. <a href="https://blog.hubspot.com/news-trends/customer-acquisition-study" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Eighty-one percent of consumers</a> trust their friends and family’s advice over any other incentive.<br></p>



<p>So give customers a reason to refer friends and family, and that alone will get you more business.</p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="Retarget-Visitors-with-a-Custom-Offer"><strong>7. Retarget Visitors with a Custom Offer</strong></h2>



<p>The best way to drive more sales is to target your visitors with personal messages.<br></p>



<p>Whether it’s in your <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-email-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">marketing emails</a>, ads, or on-site messages, personalization is the way to go.<br></p>



<p>If you’re using <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/facebook-lead-ads" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Facebook ads</a> to drive traffic to your site, you can create a custom offer for visitors who come to your site through a Facebook ad.<br></p>



<p>Smart, right?<br></p>



<p>Get creative with the copy and make sure this visitor segment knows the offer is exclusive for them—and them ONLY.<br></p>



<p>Here’s a quick example I made showing how you can do that:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="746" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Facebook-Ad-Discount-Campaign-Template-1024x746.jpg" alt="Facebook Ad Discount Campaign Template" class="wp-image-75385" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Facebook-Ad-Discount-Campaign-Template-1024x746.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Facebook-Ad-Discount-Campaign-Template-300x219.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Facebook-Ad-Discount-Campaign-Template-768x559.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Facebook-Ad-Discount-Campaign-Template-380x277.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Facebook-Ad-Discount-Campaign-Template-600x437.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Facebook-Ad-Discount-Campaign-Template-760x554.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Facebook-Ad-Discount-Campaign-Template-48x35.jpg 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Facebook-Ad-Discount-Campaign-Template-69x50.jpg 69w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Facebook-Ad-Discount-Campaign-Template-673x490.jpg 673w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Facebook-Ad-Discount-Campaign-Template-220x160.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Facebook-Ad-Discount-Campaign-Template-385x280.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Facebook-Ad-Discount-Campaign-Template.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Alternative</strong>: You can also offer a content upgrade that’s relevant to your Facebook ad and ask for an email address in exchange.<br></p>



<p>Let’s say you have a Facebook ad promoting a new line of eyeshadow.<br></p>



<p>A user clicks through to your site but isn’t ready to buy. Offer them a free guide on how to apply different types of eyeshadow for different looks and occasions. Then, include product recommendations from your new product line in the guide.<br></p>



<p>Here’s what a campaign like that could look like:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="586" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Free-Eye-Shadow-Guide-Template-1024x586.jpg" alt="Free Eye Shadow Guide Template" class="wp-image-75389" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Free-Eye-Shadow-Guide-Template-1024x586.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Free-Eye-Shadow-Guide-Template-300x172.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Free-Eye-Shadow-Guide-Template-768x440.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Free-Eye-Shadow-Guide-Template-380x218.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Free-Eye-Shadow-Guide-Template-600x344.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Free-Eye-Shadow-Guide-Template-760x435.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Free-Eye-Shadow-Guide-Template-61x35.jpg 61w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Free-Eye-Shadow-Guide-Template-87x50.jpg 87w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Free-Eye-Shadow-Guide-Template-740x424.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Free-Eye-Shadow-Guide-Template-220x126.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Free-Eye-Shadow-Guide-Template-385x220.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Free-Eye-Shadow-Guide-Template.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>
</div></div>



<h2 id="Offer-Discounts-on-Subscriptions"><strong>8. Offer Discounts on Subscriptions</strong></h2>



<p>There are many ways to improve <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/customer-retention-emails" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">customer retention</a>.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>But one of my favorites is creating a subscription for your product.<br></p>



<p>Today, consumers are looking for <em>convenience</em> above all. And the quicker and easier they can get their hands on what they need, the better.<br></p>



<p>In fact, brands like <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/harrys-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Harry’s</a>, <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/meundies-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">MeUndies</a>, and <a href="https://www.brushbox.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Brushbox</a>, to name a few, now offer subscriptions to help improve customer retention.<br></p>



<p>If you want to incentivize prospects to choose a subscription over a one-time purchase, you can offer a discount on your subscriptions.<br></p>



<p>Most companies can afford to do this because they know it will increase their customer lifetime value (LTV) and recoup it on the back end.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>MeUndies are a good example of a brand that understands the importance of continuity. In fact, they recently moved to a membership model to grow their business faster.<br></p>



<p>On their product pages, MeUndies highlight the benefits of their subscription three times, which includes a discount and exclusive membership colors:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="505" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Subscription-1024x505.png" alt="MeUndies Subscription" class="wp-image-75405" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Subscription-1024x505.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Subscription-300x148.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Subscription-768x379.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Subscription-1536x758.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Subscription-380x187.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Subscription-600x296.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Subscription-760x375.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Subscription-1440x710.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Subscription-71x35.png 71w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Subscription-101x50.png 101w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Subscription-740x365.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Subscription-220x109.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Subscription-385x190.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/MeUndies-Subscription.png 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>If you only offer subscriptions, you can use discounts to upgrade monthly subscriptions to annual subscriptions.<br></p>



<p>At Sleeknote, we offer a <a aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://sleeknote.com/pricing" target="_blank">20% discount on annual plans</a> because we know customer’s LTV increases if they choose that option.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Alternative</strong>: There are many ways to drive users to choose a subscription over a one-time purchase without offering a discount. You can offer free shipping, or focus on convenience for the user for choosing a subscription.</p>



<p>Here’s an excerpt from BeanBox’s <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-value-proposition">value proposition</a> focusing on convenience for the buyer:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="255" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/BeanBox-Value-Proposition-1024x255.jpg" alt="BeanBox Value Proposition" class="wp-image-75353" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/BeanBox-Value-Proposition-1024x255.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/BeanBox-Value-Proposition-300x75.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/BeanBox-Value-Proposition-768x191.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/BeanBox-Value-Proposition-380x95.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/BeanBox-Value-Proposition-600x150.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/BeanBox-Value-Proposition-760x189.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/BeanBox-Value-Proposition-140x35.jpg 140w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/BeanBox-Value-Proposition-201x50.jpg 201w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/BeanBox-Value-Proposition-740x184.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/BeanBox-Value-Proposition-220x55.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/BeanBox-Value-Proposition-385x96.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/BeanBox-Value-Proposition.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>
</div></div>



<h2 id="Follow-Up-with-Event-Attendees"><strong>9. Follow Up with Event Attendees</strong></h2>



<p>If you host or attend events to promote your products, there’s a lot of potential in following up with attendees after the event.<br></p>



<p>Send an email to attendees where you promote some of the products you promoted at the event. Make sure to link to a page on your site with these products.<br></p>



<p>Track the link and then add a unique campaign to your site for these visitors specifically and promote your discount.<br></p>



<p>Here’s what that could look like:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="552" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Events-Discount-Campaign-Template-1024x552.jpg" alt="Events Discount Campaign Template" class="wp-image-75381" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Events-Discount-Campaign-Template-1024x552.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Events-Discount-Campaign-Template-300x162.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Events-Discount-Campaign-Template-768x414.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Events-Discount-Campaign-Template-380x205.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Events-Discount-Campaign-Template-600x324.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Events-Discount-Campaign-Template-760x410.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Events-Discount-Campaign-Template-65x35.jpg 65w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Events-Discount-Campaign-Template-93x50.jpg 93w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Events-Discount-Campaign-Template-740x399.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Events-Discount-Campaign-Template-220x119.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Events-Discount-Campaign-Template-385x208.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Events-Discount-Campaign-Template.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>When you only discount products from the event and not all your products, the offer becomes more personal and exclusive, and therefore more attractive to this specific visitor segment.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Alternative</strong>: You can also offer a free sample or gift when your event attendees enter your site.<br></p>



<p>Here’s it’s a good idea to limit the free gift to specific product orders, or orders with a higher average value, as <a href="https://www.poopourri.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Poo Pourri</a> does:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="468" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Poo-Pourri-Free-Gift-1024x468.jpg" alt="Poo Pourri Free Gift" class="wp-image-75417" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Poo-Pourri-Free-Gift-1024x468.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Poo-Pourri-Free-Gift-300x137.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Poo-Pourri-Free-Gift-768x351.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Poo-Pourri-Free-Gift-380x174.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Poo-Pourri-Free-Gift-600x274.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Poo-Pourri-Free-Gift-760x347.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Poo-Pourri-Free-Gift-77x35.jpg 77w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Poo-Pourri-Free-Gift-109x50.jpg 109w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Poo-Pourri-Free-Gift-740x338.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Poo-Pourri-Free-Gift-220x100.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Poo-Pourri-Free-Gift-385x176.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Poo-Pourri-Free-Gift.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>
</div></div>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


