<h2><strong>Table of Contents</strong></h2>



<p><a href="#1">1. Build a Seasonal Email List</a></p>



<p><a href="#2">2. Promote Seasonal Product Categories</a></p>



<p><a href="#3">3. Build Anticipation with a Countdown Timer</a></p>



<p><a href="#4">4. Use Season-Specific Testimonials</a></p>



<p><a href="#5">5. Customize Product Guides</a></p>



<p><a href="#6">6. Create a Seasonal Game</a></p>



<p><a href="#7">7. Use Daily Offers</a></p>



<p><a href="#8">8. Stay on Top of Problems</a></p>



<p><a href="#9">9. Add Gift Wrapping at Checkout</a></p>



<h2 id="1"><strong>1. Build a Seasonal Email List</strong></h2>



<p>Building a relevant email list is important all year round.<br></p>



<p>But during specific seasons, you should capitalize on the increased traffic by tagging and segmenting new signups by seasonal interest.<br></p>



<p>That means your optin incentive should be relevant to the season so you can retarget the leads you collect with content and offers that are specific to the season.<br></p>



<p><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/black-friday-marketing-strategies" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Black Friday</a> is a perfect example of a seasonal event where building a relevant email list <em>before</em> the big day can guarantee more sales.<br></p>



<p><a href="http://www.miinto.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Miinto</a> invites visitors to join their newsletter by offering early access to Black Friday deals:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="666" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Miinto-Black-Friday-Campaign-1024x666.jpg" alt="Miinto Black Friday Campaign" class="wp-image-80369" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Miinto-Black-Friday-Campaign-1024x666.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Miinto-Black-Friday-Campaign-300x195.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Miinto-Black-Friday-Campaign-768x499.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Miinto-Black-Friday-Campaign-400x260.jpg 400w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Miinto-Black-Friday-Campaign-380x247.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Miinto-Black-Friday-Campaign-600x390.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Miinto-Black-Friday-Campaign-760x494.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Miinto-Black-Friday-Campaign-54x35.jpg 54w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Miinto-Black-Friday-Campaign-77x50.jpg 77w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Miinto-Black-Friday-Campaign-740x481.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Miinto-Black-Friday-Campaign-220x143.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Miinto-Black-Friday-Campaign-385x250.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Miinto-Black-Friday-Campaign.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Offering early access to Black Friday deals is a great incentive for this specific event. People stand in the cold for hours to get their hands on the best Black Friday deals, so getting early access via email is both valuable and convenient.<br></p>



<p>Miinto gets a relevant email list they can target with Black Friday emails and get more traffic—and sales—on this occasion.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Action Item</strong></h3>



<p>Collect emails for upcoming seasonal events by offering, early-bird discounts, sneak previews, exclusive access to deals, and more.<br></p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="2"><strong>2. Promote Seasonal Product Categories</strong></h2>



<p>Creating a smooth user journey on your site involves helping visitors find what they’re looking for.<br></p>



<p>One way to do that during specific seasons is to gather all your seasonally relevant products on one page and promote them to your visitors.<br></p>



<p>Take Mother’s Day, for example.<br></p>



<p><a href="https://www.takeoffer.dk/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Take Offer</a> carefully selects all the products that work well as Mother’s Day gifts and use a popup to promote them:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="729" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Take-Offer-Mother_s-Day-Campaign-1024x729.jpg" alt="Take Offer Mother_s Day Campaign" class="wp-image-80397" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Take-Offer-Mother_s-Day-Campaign-1024x729.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Take-Offer-Mother_s-Day-Campaign-300x214.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Take-Offer-Mother_s-Day-Campaign-768x547.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Take-Offer-Mother_s-Day-Campaign-380x270.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Take-Offer-Mother_s-Day-Campaign-600x427.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Take-Offer-Mother_s-Day-Campaign-760x541.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Take-Offer-Mother_s-Day-Campaign-49x35.jpg 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Take-Offer-Mother_s-Day-Campaign-70x50.jpg 70w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Take-Offer-Mother_s-Day-Campaign-689x490.jpg 689w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Take-Offer-Mother_s-Day-Campaign-220x157.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Take-Offer-Mother_s-Day-Campaign-385x274.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Take-Offer-Mother_s-Day-Campaign.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-text-align-center"><em>The image text reads “Remember Mother’s Day.”</em></p>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<p>The copy is cleverly written to evoke emotions in visitors—making them more likely to click through and buy.<br></p>



<p>Guiding visitors to a smaller selection of season-specific products makes it easier for visitors to choose the right gift.<br></p>



<p>Having too many choices can prolong the decision stage and maybe even prevent people from buying.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Action Item</strong></h3>



<p>Create a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/product-page-optimization" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">product page</a> including carefully selected products relevant to a season or event and promote it on the rest of your site. Giving visitors fewer choices and guiding them is a great way to increase sales during specific seasons.<br></p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="3"><strong>3. Build Anticipation with a Countdown Timer</strong></h2>



<p>There’s nothing like anticipating a big event, right?<br></p>



<p>When I was a kid, I could never sleep the night before my birthday because I was so excited. And I’m sure I wasn’t the only one.<br></p>



<p>Building anticipation for upcoming events is a great way to create hype and get people excited about what’s to come.<br></p>



<p>So, don’t forget to promote your seasonal sales ahead of time across your site. If people don’t know it’s happening, they likely won’t come back for it.<br></p>



<p>One effective way of promoting an upcoming sale is by adding a popup with a countdown timer to your site.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="600" height="339" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Summer-Sale-Countdown.gif" alt="Summer Sale Countdown" class="wp-image-80393"/></figure></div>



<p>The countdown timer is naturally attention-drawing because it triggers people’s <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/scarcity-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">FOMO</a>.<br></p>



<p>And even though this type of popup is counting down to the start of the sale, it makes the message more memorable.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Action Item</strong></h3>



<p>Promote upcoming seasonal sales or other events in a popup across your site to drive returning traffic to your site. Protip: If your site allows for saving carts, you can add a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/call-to-action" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">call-to-action</a> to this popup and ask visitors to add their favorites to their cart to save time when the sale starts.<br></p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="4"><strong>4. Use Season-Specific Testimonials to Drive More Sales</strong></h2>



<p>It’s no secret that <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/customer-testimonials" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">customer testimonials</a> drive sales.<br></p>



<p>Consumers look to each other more than ever for <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/product-recommendations" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">product recommendations</a> and quality assurance. That’s why including testimonials on your product pages can do wonders.<br></p>



<p>But what’s better is including <em>season-specific</em> product testimonials to popular products, depending on the season.<br></p>



<p>During Thanksgiving, for example, there’s likely a spike in turkey baster sales, and during Halloween, there’s a higher demand for costumes and Halloween decorations. You get the point.<br></p>



<p>So, what are season-specific testimonials?<br></p>



<p><em>They’re testimonials from customers who bought a season-specific product and mention how that product improved their experience during that season.</em><br></p>



<p>Let’s go with the Halloween example. <a href="https://www.chasing-fireflies.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Chasing Fireflies</a> have this testimonial on one of their costume product pages:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="91" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Chasing-Fireflies-Halloween-Costume-Review-1024x91.jpg" alt="Chasing Fireflies Halloween Costume Review" class="wp-image-80353" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Chasing-Fireflies-Halloween-Costume-Review-1024x91.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Chasing-Fireflies-Halloween-Costume-Review-300x27.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Chasing-Fireflies-Halloween-Costume-Review-768x68.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Chasing-Fireflies-Halloween-Costume-Review-380x34.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Chasing-Fireflies-Halloween-Costume-Review-600x54.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Chasing-Fireflies-Halloween-Costume-Review-760x68.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Chasing-Fireflies-Halloween-Costume-Review-180x16.jpg 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Chasing-Fireflies-Halloween-Costume-Review-250x22.jpg 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Chasing-Fireflies-Halloween-Costume-Review-740x66.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Chasing-Fireflies-Halloween-Costume-Review-220x20.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Chasing-Fireflies-Halloween-Costume-Review-385x34.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Chasing-Fireflies-Halloween-Costume-Review.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>When visitors are looking for a product to use for a certain occasion, having a testimonial from another customer about how the product was perfect for that same occasion, is invaluable.<br></p>



<p>(I mean, who doesn’t want people to gush over their kid because of a cute costume you bought?)<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Action Item</strong></h3>



<p>Dig into your archives and find customer testimonials that are relevant to the season and add those to your product pages.<br></p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="5"><strong>5. Customize Product Guides</strong></h2>



<p>There are many ways to help visitors find the right product on your site.<br></p>



<p>One of the most effective ones, though, is to offer product guides for specific product categories.<br></p>



<p>If you sell appliances, you can offer a guide to choosing the right washing machine, for example.<br></p>



<p>But what if there was an easy way to customize product guides to the season?<br></p>



<p>Well, there is. And you don’t have to create new product guides every time the season changes.<br></p>



<p>The trick is how you promote your product guides.<br></p>



<p>Let me give you an example.<br></p>



<p>Here’s a “standard” product guide popup:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="404" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Standard-Dress-Guide-1024x404.jpg" alt="Standard Dress Guide" class="wp-image-80389" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Standard-Dress-Guide-1024x404.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Standard-Dress-Guide-300x119.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Standard-Dress-Guide-768x303.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Standard-Dress-Guide-380x150.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Standard-Dress-Guide-600x237.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Standard-Dress-Guide-760x300.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Standard-Dress-Guide-89x35.jpg 89w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Standard-Dress-Guide-127x50.jpg 127w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Standard-Dress-Guide-740x292.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Standard-Dress-Guide-220x87.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Standard-Dress-Guide-385x152.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Standard-Dress-Guide.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>And here’s the same popup, but customized for Christmas:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="591" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Christmas-Dress-Guide-1024x591.jpg" alt="Christmas Dress Guide" class="wp-image-80357" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Christmas-Dress-Guide-1024x591.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Christmas-Dress-Guide-300x173.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Christmas-Dress-Guide-768x443.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Christmas-Dress-Guide-380x219.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Christmas-Dress-Guide-600x346.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Christmas-Dress-Guide-760x438.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Christmas-Dress-Guide-61x35.jpg 61w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Christmas-Dress-Guide-87x50.jpg 87w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Christmas-Dress-Guide-740x427.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Christmas-Dress-Guide-220x127.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Christmas-Dress-Guide-385x222.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Christmas-Dress-Guide.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Big difference, right?<br></p>



<p>The guide is the same, but by duplicating the existing popup and changing the copy and <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/popup-design-best-practices" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">design</a> to fit the season, it becomes more relevant for visitors.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Action Item</strong></h3>



<p>Customize the design and copy for your product guide popups to match the season, and you’ll create a better user experience on your site and drive more sales.<br></p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="6"><strong>6. Create a Seasonal Game</strong></h2>



<p>If you’re anything like me, you love games and competitions.<br></p>



<p>And so do many of your website visitors.<br></p>



<p>There are many seasonal events, year-round, that can be turned into competitions and games.<br></p>



<p>Easter is one of them. In many countries, it’s a tradition to go Easter egg hunting. It’s a fun activity and you can easily incorporate it online.<br></p>



<p>Just look at this example from <a href="https://www.melvin-hamilton.com/blog/find-hidden-easter-eggs-win-amazing-prizes/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Melvin &amp; Hamilton</a>:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="200" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Melvin-and-Hamilton-Easter-Egg-Hunt-1024x200.jpg" alt="Melvin and Hamilton Easter Egg Hunt" class="wp-image-80365" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Melvin-and-Hamilton-Easter-Egg-Hunt-1024x200.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Melvin-and-Hamilton-Easter-Egg-Hunt-300x59.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Melvin-and-Hamilton-Easter-Egg-Hunt-768x150.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Melvin-and-Hamilton-Easter-Egg-Hunt-380x74.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Melvin-and-Hamilton-Easter-Egg-Hunt-600x117.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Melvin-and-Hamilton-Easter-Egg-Hunt-760x148.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Melvin-and-Hamilton-Easter-Egg-Hunt-180x35.jpg 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Melvin-and-Hamilton-Easter-Egg-Hunt-250x50.jpg 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Melvin-and-Hamilton-Easter-Egg-Hunt-740x144.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Melvin-and-Hamilton-Easter-Egg-Hunt-220x43.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Melvin-and-Hamilton-Easter-Egg-Hunt-385x75.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Melvin-and-Hamilton-Easter-Egg-Hunt.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>They created an Easter egg hunt on their online shop and encourage visitors to shop for shoes while looking for hidden Easter eggs.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>When you find an egg, you get a 10% voucher. And if you use the voucher within 30 days, you enter the competition to win a premium shoe care box.<br></p>



<p>Creating an Easter egg hunt, or another seasonal game is an effective way of driving more engagement. And if you do like Melvin &amp; Hamilton and use vouchers, you also encourage purchases from visitors.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Action Item</strong></h3>



<p>Create a fun game or competition for the next upcoming seasonal event. You can create a quiz where visitors have to look for answers on your site, or you can create a “hunt” game like the Easter egg hunt. It’s up to you, and the possibilities are endless.<br></p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="7"><strong>7. Use Daily Offers</strong></h2>



<p>During longer holiday seasons it’s a good idea to invite visitors to engage with your site continuously.<br></p>



<p>One way to do so is to create daily or weekly offers for visitors.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Let’s take Christmas as an example.<br></p>



<p>You can create a Christmas Calendar with a new reward every day, as <a href="https://www.cchobby.dk/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">CC Hobby</a> does:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="326" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/CC-Hobby-Christmas-Calendar-1024x326.jpg" alt="CC Hobby Christmas Calendar" class="wp-image-80349" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/CC-Hobby-Christmas-Calendar-1024x326.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/CC-Hobby-Christmas-Calendar-300x96.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/CC-Hobby-Christmas-Calendar-768x244.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/CC-Hobby-Christmas-Calendar-380x121.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/CC-Hobby-Christmas-Calendar-600x191.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/CC-Hobby-Christmas-Calendar-760x242.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/CC-Hobby-Christmas-Calendar-110x35.jpg 110w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/CC-Hobby-Christmas-Calendar-157x50.jpg 157w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/CC-Hobby-Christmas-Calendar-740x236.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/CC-Hobby-Christmas-Calendar-220x70.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/CC-Hobby-Christmas-Calendar-385x123.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/CC-Hobby-Christmas-Calendar.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>By having a new calendar door to open every day, CC Hobby is generating returning traffic and engagement. And more engagement means higher <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/customer-loyalty-programs" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">customer loyalty</a> in the long run.<br></p>



<p>You can even use <a href="https://sleeknote.com/features/advanced-scheduling" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">advanced scheduling</a> to schedule all your Christmas popups ahead of time so you can set it and forget it.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Action Item</strong></h3>



<p>Pre-schedule daily or weekly offers for visitors during longer holiday seasons to encourage continuous engagement from visitors.<br></p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="8"><strong>8. Stay on Top of Problems</strong></h2>



<p>Seasonal events drive a lot of website traffic. And with that, comes a host of unplanned technical issues, like checkout errors, longer waiting time on support, or worse, your entire site crashing.<br></p>



<p>We never hope for these things to happen, of course, but they do.<br></p>



<p>To encourage visitors to have patience while you’re working to fix any issues, you should activate a sitewide popup informing visitors of the situation.<br></p>



<p>Here’s an example from <a href="https://www.pixizoo.dk/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Pixizoo</a> who had issues with completing payments:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="895" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pixizoo-Service-Announcement-1024x895.jpg" alt="Pixizoo Service Announcement" class="wp-image-80373" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pixizoo-Service-Announcement-1024x895.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pixizoo-Service-Announcement-300x262.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pixizoo-Service-Announcement-768x671.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pixizoo-Service-Announcement-380x332.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pixizoo-Service-Announcement-600x525.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pixizoo-Service-Announcement-760x664.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pixizoo-Service-Announcement-40x35.jpg 40w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pixizoo-Service-Announcement-57x50.jpg 57w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pixizoo-Service-Announcement-561x490.jpg 561w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pixizoo-Service-Announcement-220x192.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pixizoo-Service-Announcement-385x337.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Pixizoo-Service-Announcement.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>It may seem unnecessary but by using this popup, Pixizoo conveyed transparency and gave potential customers a reason why their payment wasn’t going through.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Giving people a reason is in many cases enough to increase their patience and keep them on the site.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Action Item</strong></h3>



<p>Don’t be afraid to let visitors know if you’re having issues on your site. Tell them you’re working to fix the issue and give them an alternative solution if you have one.&nbsp;<br></p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="9"><strong>9. Add Gift Wrapping at Checkout</strong></h2>



<p>Many seasonal events require gift shopping which is stressful for many consumers.<br></p>



<p>It’s not only stressful to try and find the perfect gift, but it’s also time-consuming to buy wrapping paper and try to wrap the present and make it look good.<br></p>



<p>So, having a gift wrapping option on your site is a great way to offer customers that little extra service and help them save some time.<br></p>



<p>Here’s <a href="https://www.maccosmetics.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">MAC Cosmetics’</a> gift-wrapping option in checkout:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="419" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Gift-Wrapping-Option-MAC-1024x419.jpg" alt="Gift Wrapping Option MAC" class="wp-image-80361" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Gift-Wrapping-Option-MAC-1024x419.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Gift-Wrapping-Option-MAC-300x123.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Gift-Wrapping-Option-MAC-768x314.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Gift-Wrapping-Option-MAC-380x155.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Gift-Wrapping-Option-MAC-600x246.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Gift-Wrapping-Option-MAC-760x311.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Gift-Wrapping-Option-MAC-86x35.jpg 86w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Gift-Wrapping-Option-MAC-122x50.jpg 122w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Gift-Wrapping-Option-MAC-740x303.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Gift-Wrapping-Option-MAC-220x90.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Gift-Wrapping-Option-MAC-385x158.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Gift-Wrapping-Option-MAC.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>It’s a simple checkbox and previews what the gift will look like. This is great for ensuring customers the wrapping will meet their expectations.<br></p>



<p>MAC Cosmetics has this gift wrapping option all year which is even better than only having it seasonally.<br></p>



<p>It’s small things like this that customers will remember—and come back for.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Action Item</strong></h3>



<p>Add a gift wrapping option to your <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/checkout-optimization" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">checkout</a> and give customers that little extra service. It’s a small effort to make to get loyal and happy customers.<br></p>
</div></div>
</div></div>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


