<h2 id="1"><strong>1. The Upsell Email</strong></h2>



<p><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/upselling" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Upselling</a> is nothing new.</p>



<p>Many online retailers use upselling to increase the average order value for new and returning customers. But how one approaches upselling varies from business to business.</p>



<p>One brand that has created a powerful upselling strategy is <a href="https://www.meundies.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">MeUndies</a>.</p>



<p>They’ve created a continuity program, or an ascension ladder, if you will, by offering a paid membership.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="263" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/MeUndies-Membership-Model-1024x263.jpg" alt="MeUndies Membership Model" class="wp-image-91127" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/MeUndies-Membership-Model-1024x263.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/MeUndies-Membership-Model-300x77.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/MeUndies-Membership-Model-768x197.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/MeUndies-Membership-Model-380x98.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/MeUndies-Membership-Model-600x154.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/MeUndies-Membership-Model-760x195.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/MeUndies-Membership-Model-136x35.jpg 136w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/MeUndies-Membership-Model-195x50.jpg 195w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/MeUndies-Membership-Model-740x190.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/MeUndies-Membership-Model-220x56.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/MeUndies-Membership-Model-385x99.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/MeUndies-Membership-Model.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Here’s an example of a recent email promoting their membership:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="571" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/MeUndies-571x1024.jpg" alt="MeUndies" class="wp-image-91135" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/MeUndies-571x1024.jpg 571w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/MeUndies-167x300.jpg 167w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/MeUndies-380x681.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/MeUndies-20x35.jpg 20w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/MeUndies-28x50.jpg 28w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/MeUndies-273x490.jpg 273w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/MeUndies-220x395.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/MeUndies-385x690.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/MeUndies.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 571px) 100vw, 571px" /></figure></div>



<p>One way they’re able to increase their click-through rate is by offering “Member-Exclusive Prints,” which, of course, triggers <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/scarcity-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">scarcity</a> due to their limited availability.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Creating an ascension ladder and inviting customers to “ascend” to higher levels through email increases retention for a few reasons.&nbsp;</p>



<p>First, it saves customers money in the long-term. Second, it increases brand advocacy. With higher spending comes greater <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/customer-loyalty-programs" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">loyalty</a>, and that, in turn, reducing the likelihood they’ll switch to a competitor.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Takeaway&nbsp;</strong></h3>



<p>Consider a membership model to increase your customers’ lifetime value (LTV). Then, promote your membership via email and invite new and returning customers to become brand loyalists.</p>
</div></div>





<h2 id="2"><strong>2. The Birthday Email</strong></h2>



<p>If you’re anything like me, you LOVE birthdays, because, let’s be honest, it’s all about receiving presents.&nbsp;</p>



<p>People love gifts, whether they’re from friends or otherwise, so adding a surprise to a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/happy-birthday-email-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">birthday email</a> is a powerful retention incentive to use to your advantage.</p>



<p>Take this example from <a href="https://www.kikki-k.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Kikki.K</a>:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="473" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Kikki.K-Birthday-Email-473x1024.jpg" alt="Kikki.K Birthday Email" class="wp-image-91111" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Kikki.K-Birthday-Email-473x1024.jpg 473w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Kikki.K-Birthday-Email-139x300.jpg 139w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Kikki.K-Birthday-Email-768x1662.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Kikki.K-Birthday-Email-710x1536.jpg 710w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Kikki.K-Birthday-Email-946x2048.jpg 946w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Kikki.K-Birthday-Email-380x822.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Kikki.K-Birthday-Email-600x1299.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Kikki.K-Birthday-Email-760x1645.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Kikki.K-Birthday-Email-16x35.jpg 16w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Kikki.K-Birthday-Email-23x50.jpg 23w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Kikki.K-Birthday-Email-226x490.jpg 226w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Kikki.K-Birthday-Email-220x476.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Kikki.K-Birthday-Email-385x833.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Kikki.K-Birthday-Email-scaled.jpg 1183w" sizes="(max-width: 473px) 100vw, 473px" /></figure></div>



<p>To make their customers’ birthday even more special, Kikki.K offers a $10 birthday voucher and personalized <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/product-recommendations" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">product recommendations</a>.&nbsp;</p>



<p>But that’s not the only reason they do it.</p>



<p>Think about it for a moment. One of the most common gifts to give on birthdays is money. Would you not rather spend your birthday money on a brand that acknowledges the celebration AND offers suggestions on what to spend that money on?</p>



<p>I know I would.</p>



<p>The birthday email is becoming more common, but that doesn’t mean it’s becoming less effective. It’s still a pleasant surprise in your customer’s inbox, and it’s the type of email that your customers remember.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Takeaway&nbsp;</strong></h3>



<p>Let your customers know you appreciate them on their special day. You don’t have to make grand gestures or even offer <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/discount-strategy" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">discounts</a>. But keep in mind that most people accept even the smallest gestures with gratitude.</p>
</div></div>





<h2 id="3"><strong>3. The Special Occasions Email</strong></h2>



<p>A big part of retaining existing customers is ensuring your brand stays top of mind&#8230;</p>



<p>&#8230;And that means reaching out to buyers regularly with relevant, personalized content.</p>



<p>One way to do that is to send emails on special occasions like Valentine’s Day, Father’s Day, Mother’s Day, and more.</p>



<p>A week before Mother’s Day, I got this email from <a href="https://www.happysocks.com/us/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Happy Socks</a>:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="551" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Happy-Socks-Retention-Email-551x1024.jpg" alt="Happy Socks Retention Email" class="wp-image-91103" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Happy-Socks-Retention-Email-551x1024.jpg 551w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Happy-Socks-Retention-Email-161x300.jpg 161w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Happy-Socks-Retention-Email-768x1427.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Happy-Socks-Retention-Email-827x1536.jpg 827w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Happy-Socks-Retention-Email-1102x2048.jpg 1102w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Happy-Socks-Retention-Email-380x706.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Happy-Socks-Retention-Email-600x1115.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Happy-Socks-Retention-Email-760x1412.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Happy-Socks-Retention-Email-19x35.jpg 19w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Happy-Socks-Retention-Email-27x50.jpg 27w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Happy-Socks-Retention-Email-264x490.jpg 264w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Happy-Socks-Retention-Email-220x409.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Happy-Socks-Retention-Email-385x715.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Happy-Socks-Retention-Email.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 551px) 100vw, 551px" /></figure></div>



<p>There are a few reasons this email works well:</p>



<ol><li><strong>It’s relevant.</strong> Happy Socks sent the email about a week before Mother’s Day to ensure potential buyers had time to order and receive the product in time for Mother’s Day.</li><li><strong>It’s eye-catching.</strong> They included moving images with bold colors and patterns.</li><li><strong>It gives value.</strong> Happy Socks offered free shipping, which worked as an added incentive for prospects to buy.</li><li><strong>It’s exclusive. </strong>Notice how Happy Socks had designed products specifically for this occasion? This added to the product’s exclusivity and acted as another incentive to buy.</li></ol>



<p>You can use this type of email for all kinds of occasions. Heck, you can even create your own brand-specific occasions and celebrate them with your audience. (I’m still trying to get the Sleeknote team on board with National Sleeknote Puppy Day.)</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Takeaway&nbsp;</strong></h3>



<p>Use the special occasions email to remind your audience that you’re still here and offer value that’s relevant to a specific occasion.</p>
</div></div>





<h2 id="4"><strong>4. The Scheduled Reminder Email</strong></h2>



<p>The reminder email is essentially a special occasions email. But I think it deserves its own category based on a unique example I came across when writing <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/man-crates-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">my post on Man Crates</a>.</p>



<p>It’s not the email itself that’s groundbreaking. Rather, it’s the basis from which it’s sent.</p>



<p>How often have you forgotten an anniversary or a birthday and had to rush out to find a last-minute gift? I know I have. But as a business, you don’t know when to remind your audience of these occasions—unless you ask:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="530" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Thank-You-Page-1024x530.jpg" alt="Man Crates Thank You Page" class="wp-image-91123" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Thank-You-Page-1024x530.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Thank-You-Page-300x155.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Thank-You-Page-768x397.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Thank-You-Page-380x197.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Thank-You-Page-600x311.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Thank-You-Page-760x393.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Thank-You-Page-68x35.jpg 68w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Thank-You-Page-97x50.jpg 97w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Thank-You-Page-740x383.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Thank-You-Page-220x114.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Thank-You-Page-385x199.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Thank-You-Page.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Using a 10% discount as an incentive, <a href="https://www.mancrates.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Man Crates</a> invites customers to create reminders for special occasions on their <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/thank-you-page" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">thank you page</a>. It’s a great way to use reciprocity. Give something; get something. Then, when it’s time, Man Crates deliver on their promise and send you a reminder email.</p>



<p>Here’s the <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/email-subject-lines" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">subject line</a>:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="92" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Subject-Line-1024x92.jpg" alt="Man Crates Subject Line" class="wp-image-91119" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Subject-Line-1024x92.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Subject-Line-300x27.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Subject-Line-768x69.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Subject-Line-380x34.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Subject-Line-600x54.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Subject-Line-760x68.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Subject-Line-180x16.jpg 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Subject-Line-250x23.jpg 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Subject-Line-740x67.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Subject-Line-220x20.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Subject-Line-385x35.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Subject-Line.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Followed by the body:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="744" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Reminder-Email-744x1024.jpg" alt="Man Crates Reminder Email" class="wp-image-91115" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Reminder-Email-744x1024.jpg 744w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Reminder-Email-218x300.jpg 218w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Reminder-Email-768x1057.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Reminder-Email-1116x1536.jpg 1116w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Reminder-Email-380x523.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Reminder-Email-600x826.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Reminder-Email-760x1046.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Reminder-Email-25x35.jpg 25w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Reminder-Email-36x50.jpg 36w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Reminder-Email-356x490.jpg 356w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Reminder-Email-220x303.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Reminder-Email-385x530.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Man-Crates-Reminder-Email.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 744px) 100vw, 744px" /></figure></div>



<p>It’s simple, yet effective, and best of all, easy to apply to your business.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Takeaway&nbsp;</strong></h3>



<p>Ask customers to set reminders for any type of occasion where they would be interested in buying from you. Then, add an extra incentive (such as a discount) to your reminder email. Even if they don’t buy, you will keep your brand top of mind.</p>
</div></div>





<h2 id="5"><strong>5. The Anniversary Email</strong></h2>



<p>Who doesn’t like a good celebration? I know I do. Celebrating anniversaries can help build stronger relationships with customers and give them a reason to stay with you.</p>



<p>One of the reasons anniversary emails work so well is that they’re <em>unexpected.</em> It’s rare to see businesses celebrate their customers’ anniversaries, which makes them stand out more in the inbox. And if they’re well-written, they put a smile on your customers’ faces and get them to take action in your email.</p>



<p>I recently got this email from <a href="https://www.chubbiesshorts.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Chubbies</a>, celebrating that it was exactly two years ago I joined the Chubbies family:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="671" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chubbies-Anniversary-Email-671x1024.jpg" alt="Chubbies-Anniversary-Email" class="wp-image-91083" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chubbies-Anniversary-Email-671x1024.jpg 671w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chubbies-Anniversary-Email-197x300.jpg 197w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chubbies-Anniversary-Email-768x1172.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chubbies-Anniversary-Email-380x580.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chubbies-Anniversary-Email-600x916.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chubbies-Anniversary-Email-760x1160.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chubbies-Anniversary-Email-23x35.jpg 23w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chubbies-Anniversary-Email-33x50.jpg 33w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chubbies-Anniversary-Email-321x490.jpg 321w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chubbies-Anniversary-Email-220x336.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chubbies-Anniversary-Email-385x588.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chubbies-Anniversary-Email.jpg 800w" sizes="(max-width: 671px) 100vw, 671px" /></figure></div>



<p>Reading this email put a huge smile on my face for multiple reasons:</p>



<ol><li>They wished me a happy anniversary and piqued my interest right away;</li><li>They included a photo that supported the message and increased the “party-feeling” in the email;</li><li>They included a small reward of $5 to spend on my next purchase.</li></ol>



<p>It might be a small token of appreciation, but in this case, the thought meant something.</p>



<p>The rare and unique emails are those you will remember.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Takeaway</strong></h3>



<p>Think about what anniversaries you can celebrate with your audience. It could be one year of being subscribed to an email list, a month of using your product, or a third thing. Make your audience feel special and celebrate with them whenever you can.</p>
</div></div>





<h2 id="6"><strong>6. The Reminder Email (with a Twist)</strong></h2>



<p>The reminder email is a great retention email because it encourages customers to buy again without feeling pressured.</p>



<p>After a customer buys something, you can <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/product-recommendations" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">recommend additional products</a> to help them get the full product experience.</p>



<p>For example, if a customer buys a new TV, you can suggest adding surround sound speakers to make the most out of their new TV.</p>



<p>Or, if you sell experiences, you can do as <a href="https://www.tripadvisor.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Tripadvisor</a> does and suggest other experiences in the area the customer might like.</p>



<p>To borrow a personal example, I recently visited my sister in Hawaii and booked a helicopter tour on Maui.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="816" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Helicopter-Tour-816x1024.jpg" alt="Helicopter Tour" class="wp-image-91107" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Helicopter-Tour-816x1024.jpg 816w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Helicopter-Tour-239x300.jpg 239w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Helicopter-Tour-768x963.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Helicopter-Tour-380x477.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Helicopter-Tour-600x753.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Helicopter-Tour-760x953.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Helicopter-Tour-28x35.jpg 28w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Helicopter-Tour-40x50.jpg 40w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Helicopter-Tour-391x490.jpg 391w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Helicopter-Tour-220x276.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Helicopter-Tour-385x483.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Helicopter-Tour.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 816px) 100vw, 816px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-text-align-center"><em>Us before takeoff.</em></p>





<p>A few days before the planned helicopter tour, I received this email:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="669" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Trip-Advisor-Email-1-669x1024.jpg" alt="Trip Advisor Email 1" class="wp-image-91147" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Trip-Advisor-Email-1-669x1024.jpg 669w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Trip-Advisor-Email-1-196x300.jpg 196w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Trip-Advisor-Email-1-768x1175.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Trip-Advisor-Email-1-1004x1536.jpg 1004w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Trip-Advisor-Email-1-380x581.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Trip-Advisor-Email-1-600x918.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Trip-Advisor-Email-1-760x1163.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Trip-Advisor-Email-1-23x35.jpg 23w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Trip-Advisor-Email-1-33x50.jpg 33w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Trip-Advisor-Email-1-320x490.jpg 320w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Trip-Advisor-Email-1-220x337.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Trip-Advisor-Email-1-385x589.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Trip-Advisor-Email-1.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 669px) 100vw, 669px" /></figure></div>



<p>But that’s not all. Part of the email included recommendations for other experiences on Maui based on what other people had booked in addition to the helicopter tour:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="671" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/TripAdvisor-Email-2-671x1024.jpg" alt="TripAdvisor Email 2" class="wp-image-91151" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/TripAdvisor-Email-2-671x1024.jpg 671w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/TripAdvisor-Email-2-197x300.jpg 197w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/TripAdvisor-Email-2-768x1172.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/TripAdvisor-Email-2-1007x1536.jpg 1007w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/TripAdvisor-Email-2-380x580.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/TripAdvisor-Email-2-600x916.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/TripAdvisor-Email-2-760x1160.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/TripAdvisor-Email-2-23x35.jpg 23w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/TripAdvisor-Email-2-33x50.jpg 33w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/TripAdvisor-Email-2-321x490.jpg 321w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/TripAdvisor-Email-2-220x336.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/TripAdvisor-Email-2-385x587.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/TripAdvisor-Email-2.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 671px) 100vw, 671px" /></figure></div>



<p>Recommending relevant products that complement recent purchases is a great way to boost revenue and invite customers to come back to your store.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Takeaway&nbsp;</strong></h3>



<p>Tempt customers with other products that go well with past purchases to give them a better experience.</p>
</div></div>





<h2 id="7"><strong>7. The Feedback Email</strong></h2>



<p>The feedback email is an essential part of any retention strategy.</p>



<p>The goal is to ask customers for <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/customer-feedback" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">feedback</a> on their recent purchases to keep them engaged—and promote your best products. It’s a no-brainer.</p>



<p>Here’s an example I stumbled upon when researching my article on <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/sunski-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Sunski</a>:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="812" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sunski-Review-Email-812x1024.jpg" alt="Sunski Review Email" class="wp-image-91139" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sunski-Review-Email-812x1024.jpg 812w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sunski-Review-Email-238x300.jpg 238w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sunski-Review-Email-768x969.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sunski-Review-Email-380x479.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sunski-Review-Email-600x757.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sunski-Review-Email-760x959.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sunski-Review-Email-28x35.jpg 28w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sunski-Review-Email-40x50.jpg 40w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sunski-Review-Email-388x490.jpg 388w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sunski-Review-Email-220x278.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sunski-Review-Email-385x486.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sunski-Review-Email.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 812px) 100vw, 812px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.sunski.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Sunski</a> uses radio buttons to make it easy for customers to rate the product. From there, customers can expand on their ratings by writing a review below.</p>



<p>When scheduling a feedback email, send it a few days after a customer has received their purchase. Doing so gives customers enough time to try the product as their purchase is still fresh in their minds.</p>



<p>Furthermore, when you ask for feedback, you invite your customers to think about the product they bought from you–even if they don’t submit any feedback.</p>



<p>Doing so keeps your brand top of mind for longer, making it more likely these customers will return to your site and buy again (if they were satisfied with the product, of course).</p>



<p>And if your customers submit reviews, they automatically become brand advocates because they’re adding their stamp of approval of your product for the world to see.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Takeaway&nbsp;</strong></h3>



<p>Invite customers to review their purchase after they’ve received and used it. Then, repurpose the best reviews in your marketing for <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/social-proof" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">social proof</a>.</p>
</div></div>





<h2 id="8"><strong>8. The Thank You Email</strong></h2>



<p>A thank you or a thumbs up, without any hidden agendas can work wonders when it comes to retaining your customers.</p>



<p>Let’s give it a try:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="700" height="550" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Thumbs-Up-700px.gif" alt="Thumbs Up 700px" class="wp-image-91143"/></figure></div>



<p>Made you feel pretty good, huh?</p>



<p>A thumbs up or a pat on the back makes us smile—and that’s exactly the reaction you want from your customers.</p>



<p>The most effective emails are those that evoke feelings in the receiver.</p>



<p>So, why not email your customers telling them how awesome they are?</p>



<p>Here’s how <a href="https://www.bando.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Ban.do</a> does it:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="606" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Ban.do-Thank-You-Email-606x1024.jpg" alt="Ban.do Thank You Email" class="wp-image-91071" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Ban.do-Thank-You-Email-606x1024.jpg 606w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Ban.do-Thank-You-Email-178x300.jpg 178w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Ban.do-Thank-You-Email-768x1297.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Ban.do-Thank-You-Email-909x1536.jpg 909w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Ban.do-Thank-You-Email-380x642.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Ban.do-Thank-You-Email-600x1014.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Ban.do-Thank-You-Email-760x1284.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Ban.do-Thank-You-Email-21x35.jpg 21w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Ban.do-Thank-You-Email-30x50.jpg 30w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Ban.do-Thank-You-Email-290x490.jpg 290w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Ban.do-Thank-You-Email-220x372.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Ban.do-Thank-You-Email-385x650.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Ban.do-Thank-You-Email.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 606px) 100vw, 606px" /></figure></div>



<p>There’s no <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/email-call-to-action" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">call-to-action</a> or hidden agenda. Just a thank you to customers for buying and supporting their mission.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Takeaway&nbsp;</strong></h3>



<p>Remember to thank your customers every once in a while. They’re the reason your business is alive, after all.<strong> </strong>Make them feel good about your brand, and they’re yours for life. (Okay, that might be an exaggeration, but you get my point.)</p>
</div></div>





<h2 id="9"><strong>9. The Win-Back Email</strong></h2>



<p>Disengaged customers are an inevitable reality for marketers.</p>



<p>Customers who previously bought from before disappear for one reason or another. They lose interest, forget about your business, or worse, move on to a competitor.</p>



<p>But not all is lost.&nbsp;</p>



<p>This is where the win-back email comes into play.</p>



<p>With it, you can remind customers of why they chose your business, to begin with, and, hopefully, convince them to return.</p>



<p><a href="https://www.brooklinen.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Brooklinen</a>, for example, gives its customers three reasons to return to their site:</p>



<ol><li>Urgency;</li><li>Customer satisfaction; and</li><li>Great quality for low prices.</li></ol>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="730" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Email-1-1-730x1024.jpg" alt="Brooklinen Email 1" class="wp-image-91075" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Email-1-1-730x1024.jpg 730w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Email-1-1-214x300.jpg 214w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Email-1-1-768x1078.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Email-1-1-1095x1536.jpg 1095w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Email-1-1-380x533.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Email-1-1-600x842.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Email-1-1-760x1067.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Email-1-1-25x35.jpg 25w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Email-1-1-36x50.jpg 36w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Email-1-1-349x490.jpg 349w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Email-1-1-220x309.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Email-1-1-385x540.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Email-1-1.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 730px) 100vw, 730px" /></figure></div>



<p>And if, as a former customer, Brooklinen don’t convince you, the second half of the email might do:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="649" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Email-2-1-649x1024.jpg" alt="Brooklinen Email 2" class="wp-image-91079" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Email-2-1-649x1024.jpg 649w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Email-2-1-190x300.jpg 190w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Email-2-1-768x1212.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Email-2-1-973x1536.jpg 973w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Email-2-1-380x600.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Email-2-1-600x947.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Email-2-1-760x1200.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Email-2-1-22x35.jpg 22w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Email-2-1-32x50.jpg 32w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Email-2-1-310x490.jpg 310w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Email-2-1-220x347.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Email-2-1-385x608.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Brooklinen-Email-2-1.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 649px) 100vw, 649px" /></figure></div>



<p>They offer a gift with your order and give you product suggestions to help you choose what to buy.</p>



<p>What more could you want?</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Takeaway&nbsp;</strong></h3>



<p>Identify “at-risk” customers who haven’t bought from you in a long time. Send them an email and remind them of your business values and give them an incentive to return to your site.&nbsp;</p>
</div></div>




