<h2><strong>Conclusion</strong></h2>



<p>Yes, acquiring new customers is important. But so, too, is continuing to nurture existing buyers.</p>



<p>I’ve given you nine customer retention strategies. Not all will be relevant to your business. And that’s okay. But those that are will remind existing customers that you’re worth committing to.</p>



<p>And that’s only a good thing.</p>



