<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>Scarcity Marketing: 6 Innovative Tactics You Need to Know (+ Examples)</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/category/email-marketing" rel="category tag">Email Marketing</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="240" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Scarcity-Marketing-Wordpress-1-1024x240.jpg" alt="Scarcity Marketing [Wordpress]" class="wp-image-82248" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Scarcity-Marketing-Wordpress-1-1024x240.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Scarcity-Marketing-Wordpress-1-300x70.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Scarcity-Marketing-Wordpress-1-768x180.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Scarcity-Marketing-Wordpress-1-1536x360.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Scarcity-Marketing-Wordpress-1-2048x480.jpg 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Scarcity-Marketing-Wordpress-1-380x89.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Scarcity-Marketing-Wordpress-1-600x141.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Scarcity-Marketing-Wordpress-1-760x178.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Scarcity-Marketing-Wordpress-1-1440x338.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Scarcity-Marketing-Wordpress-1-149x35.jpg 149w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Scarcity-Marketing-Wordpress-1-213x50.jpg 213w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Scarcity-Marketing-Wordpress-1-740x173.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Scarcity-Marketing-Wordpress-1-220x52.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Scarcity-Marketing-Wordpress-1-385x90.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_5e822305e3572" class="block-preamble"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">It’s no secret: Scarcity marketing works. People always want what they can’t have because they think the grass is greener on the other side.<br data-rich-text-line-break="true" /></span></p>
</div>






<p>Many marketers are already using scarcity in their email marketing, but only a few are using it <em>right</em>.<br></p>



<p>If you’re using scarcity in your marketing, chances are I’m talking about <em>you</em>.<br></p>



<p>One misconception with scarcity is that you need a good discount to get readers to act.<br></p>



<p>Wrong.<br></p>



<p>In this article, I’ll show you six killer scarcity example for email so you can increase your ROI (without resorting to sleezy marketing tactics).<br></p>


