<h1 class="has-text-align-center"> Email Copywriting 101: How to Write Mouthwateringly Good Marketing Emails </h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/category/email-marketing" rel="category tag">Email Marketing</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="240" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Email-Copywriting-Wordpress-1-1024x240.jpg" alt="Email Copywriting (WordPress)" class="wp-image-76012" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Email-Copywriting-Wordpress-1-1024x240.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Email-Copywriting-Wordpress-1-300x70.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Email-Copywriting-Wordpress-1-768x180.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Email-Copywriting-Wordpress-1-1536x360.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Email-Copywriting-Wordpress-1-2048x480.jpg 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Email-Copywriting-Wordpress-1-380x89.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Email-Copywriting-Wordpress-1-600x141.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Email-Copywriting-Wordpress-1-760x178.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Email-Copywriting-Wordpress-1-1440x338.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Email-Copywriting-Wordpress-1-149x35.jpg 149w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Email-Copywriting-Wordpress-1-213x50.jpg 213w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Email-Copywriting-Wordpress-1-740x173.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Email-Copywriting-Wordpress-1-220x52.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Email-Copywriting-Wordpress-1-385x90.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_5e7877b22d1da" class="block-preamble"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">It’s a well-known feeling among marketers… You’re trying to write an email campaign for our email list but you just can’t seem to find the right angle.</span></p>
</div>






<p>If this sounds familiar—keep reading.<br></p>



<p>Today, marketers struggle to write email copy that gets their emails opened and invites readers to take action.<br></p>



<p>The truth is&#8230;<br></p>



<p>Email <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/copywriting-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">copywriting</a> isn’t just about the subject line&#8230;&nbsp;</p>



<p>It’s not just about the call-to-action&#8230;&nbsp;</p>



<p>And it’s not just about the copy&#8230;<br></p>



<p>It’s about all of it, and creating emails that function as automated selling machines from the moment you click send.<br></p>



<p>And that’s what I’m going to show you today: how to write effective emails that resonate with your audience that drive them to take action—meaning more money in the bank for you.<br></p>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5e6f3eb323036" class="block-content-upgrade">
